\id MRK - Abureni 
\h Amaki̠ 
\toc1 Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ Amaki̠ Age̠ Bho̠ 
\toc2 Amaki̠ 
\toc3 Amak 
\mt2 Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ 
\mt1 Amaki̠ 
\mt2 Age̠ Bho̠ 
\imt1 Otighom 
\ip Amaki̠ wa̠ ubhelegi nyen ma̠ Azo̠n Amaki̠ bho̠, age̠ ma̠ A̠d̠ire onon. I̠na bo̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal Ogbogir bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Apo̠l na̠ Abanabas d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r e̠gi̠ o̠gba asu̠gbagba bho̠ (Rogir 13:13). Ubhin ma̠a̠, asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ibom asu̠gbagba ta̠ A̠pita̠ ya̠ i̠na age̠ a̠kokod̠i bho̠. Agu̠b̠an ka̠ Amaki̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r a̠d̠ire Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ i̠na age̠ ma ilologia̠n ya̠ ib̠uiy ipu ma̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba iyed̠i. I̠na na̠ o̠gba ani̠ d̠o̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ i̠mara ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, ya̠a̠ a̠b̠eton d̠a̠ owura̠ amu̠m bho̠ sekina̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. I̠na age̠ d̠a̠ a̠duom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ofenymeni a̠nwunom ta̠ Akrai̠st ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠rom bho̠ na̠ o̠gba omutiom ma̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s bha̠ Akrai̠st bho̠. I̠na agba asi̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, bha̠ Ob̠a̠ra̠motu sekina̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ga̠i sa̠ age̠ a̠gboloma̠ nyen ogir na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠. A̠d̠ire bho̠ a̠kunugiom d̠a̠ omugh na̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ a̠bhin a̠muzughod̠iom rebu ebu a̠ghud̠um ta̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st. 
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ 
\io1 Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ na̠ owuramu̠m ta̠ A̠zizo̠s \ior (1:1-13) \ior* 
\io1 Ogir wa̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Agalili bho̠ \ior (1:14—9:50) \ior* 
\io1 O̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m na̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ \ior (10:1—11:25) \ior* 
\io1 Asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an d̠a̠ e̠ma A̠zeruse̠le̠m \ior (11:27—12:44) \ior* 
\io1 Iwowa̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ eru \ior (13:1-37) \ior* 
\io1 Omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ \ior (14:1—16:20)\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Asu̠gbagba ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 3:1-12; A̠luk 3:1-18; Azo̠n 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Onon agu̠o̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin ake̠ bho̠.  
\v 2 D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire ta̠ owil Ai̠zaya bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “Nagha o! Ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ d̠ami̠ a̠ruom o̠ni̠ a̠duom, 
\q2 ma̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man eten bho̠ ob̠a̠ra̠ oyom.” 
\q1  
\v 3 “Okoroko na̠ a̠si na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ e̠sala a̠de i̠si̠sar bho̠, ma̠a̠, 
\q1 ‘I̠tu̠ghu̠mane̠ ma̠ eten bho̠ ma̠ esisia̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, 
\q2 ma̠ eselegi ma̠ reten bho̠.’”\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Azaya 40:3\x* 
\m  
\v 4 Sa̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ e̠sala a̠de i̠si̠sar bho̠, sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, a̠nwunom etiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa ewura̠ ma̠ amu̠m, sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠awa.  
\v 5 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh A̠zudia̠ sekina̠ a̠nwunom A̠zeruse̠le̠m id̠u i̠gi̠ do̠yo̠. Sa̠ awa i̠gba ma̠ i̠karabh d̠awa imutiom, sa̠ i̠na a̠wur awa ma̠ amu̠m d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan.  
\v 6 Azo̠n a̠bura̠ ma̠ ibura̠ ya̠ ubhin ipur e̠nam-a̠dol \f + \fr 1:6 \ft e̠nam-a̠dol (e̠nam e̠kpu̠aman) \f*u̠le̠m, sa̠ i̠na akpo̠aghan o̠kara ozu e̠nam d̠a̠ eka̠ka̠gh d̠o̠yo̠. Ed̠ia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ bha̠ i̠ganw na̠ ame̠ ya̠ od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ aparapa.  
\v 7 Sa̠ Azo̠n agba ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ aman d̠ami̠ bho̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ami̠, ya̠a̠ ami̠ ilei d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ozuma̠n o̠ko̠gi̠o̠n id̠id̠igh ragbaka do̠yo̠.  
\v 8 Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin amu̠m na̠ a̠wur inyin, ya̠a̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠wur inyin.” 
\s1 Owur amu̠m ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 3:13; A̠luk 3:21-22; 4:1-13) 
\p  
\v 9 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, a̠zuzua̠n ola̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Anazare̠t d̠a̠ ebhugh Agalili ka̠ ate̠i̠ Azo̠n. Sa̠ Azo̠n a̠wur i̠na ma̠ amu̠m d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan.  
\v 10 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠bhun bho̠ sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh ka̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠gurona̠, sa̠ E̠mu̠gh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠sor ra̠ akpasan i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ okur osege.  
\v 11 Sa̠ okoroko a̠si a̠mite d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ma̠a̠: “Anwa o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, wa̠ ami̠ itula̠n ibom bho̠, wa̠ ologi d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠bhon na̠ a̠ni̠gha̠ bho̠.” 
\s1 Ad̠agi̠an ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 4:1-11; A̠luk 4:1-13) 
\p  
\v 12 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠ sa̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠rileghom i̠na ka̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ e̠sala a̠de i̠si̠sar.  
\v 13 I̠na aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ d̠a̠ e̠sala a̠de i̠si̠sar bho̠ ma̠ eruba̠l ra̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ Eru Bho̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠na. A̠zizo̠s aro̠ na̠ i̠nam ed̠um, sa̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ iru ra̠ i̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ inigha̠ i̠na. 
\s1 O̠pu̠r o̠ke̠ ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ Agalili 
\r (Amatiu 4:12-22; A̠luk 4:14-15; 5:1-11) 
\p  
\v 14 Igiel bho̠ na̠ ob̠ol Azo̠n o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ ikoli bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili ka̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,  
\v 15 sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Na̠ ate̠i̠ obhel wa̠ omuzoghod̠iom bho̠, i̠rileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n. Itiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh, ma̠ ed̠umom ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠!”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi ma̠ i̠pu̠r Ogbo-atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rile agbal Abadi̠ Agalili, sa̠ abi̠gh i̠wal a̠rumor, Asai̠mo̠n na̠ Anduru umor d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ awa na̠ erobh o̠gbo̠ d̠a̠ abadi̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa i̠ku̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠.  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “I̠tu̠o̠no̠me̠ Ami̠, sa̠ Ami̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni inyin i̠ku̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠ a̠nwunom.”  
\v 18 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠ sa̠ awa i̠we̠le̠man i̠gbo̠ d̠awa i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 19 O̠d̠u̠a i̠se̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh A̠zemsi o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Aze̠bidi na̠ Azo̠n umor d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ologi oghugh na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠man i̠gbo̠ d̠awa.  
\v 20 Ogbo na̠ onin sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi awa, sa̠ awa i̠we̠le̠ epa̠ ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠awa Aze̠bidi d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠ na̠ ipa̠n ogbo ogir ya̠ awa i̠ko̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh 
\r (A̠luk 4:31-37) 
\p  
\v 21 Awa i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m, sa̠ ate̠i̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.  
\v 22 Ed̠igh ilologia̠n a̠nwunom o̠mu̠gho̠n atu̠ghu̠me̠ni d̠o̠yo̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠, i̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ita̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ roloko bho̠.  
\v 23 Odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠nyegi, aro̠ d̠a̠ ologi otu u̠gala bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin obom okoroko a̠mulughu. Sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠,  
\v 24 “Anwa na̠ i̠yar ka̠ unwuna̠ ma̠ ere, A̠zizo̠s Anazare̠t? Anwa na̠ a̠ru ra̠ o̠pi̠e̠gi̠ i̠yar o̠man ke̠re̠? I̠yar ologhom ma̠a̠ anwa We̠b̠ab̠ala wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin a̠ru bho̠!”  
\v 25 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s aghaghana i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m! Mite d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠!”  
\v 26 Sa̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠teb̠eli i̠na, sa̠ i̠na asalaghu̠ a̠mulughu na̠ obom o̠kparakpar okoroko ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 27 Sa̠ abar bho̠ a̠d̠igh eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ ilologia̠n, sa̠ awa imogha̠, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠pura̠n odi ma̠a̠, “Woo, onon ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠! I̠na na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ na̠ aghaghana ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh, sa̠ awa na̠ e̠nagha i̠na.”  
\v 28 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ o̠du̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s asi̠saragi̠an ka̠ ate̠i̠ kesi kesi d̠a̠ ebhugh Agalili. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom 
\r (Amatiu 8:14-17; A̠luk 4:38-41) 
\p  
\v 29 Awa i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ otu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin A̠zemsi̠ na̠ Azo̠n agi̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n na̠ Anduru.  
\v 30 D̠a̠ obhel bho̠ awa i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh o̠yo̠go̠-onweni ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n d̠a̠ e̠mana na̠ asu̠nwe̠r amu̠m o̠bhi̠i̠y na̠ a̠sibh i̠na, sa̠ awa i̠nu̠r i̠gba i̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 31 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ ka̠ a̠sibh ani̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠b̠eton, sa̠ amu̠m-o̠bhi̠i̠y bho̠ ad̠u̠a, sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ed̠ia̠n aki̠o̠m awa.  
\v 32 Ate̠i̠ a̠dule d̠a̠ obhel ogogo bho̠ na̠ a̠d̠ugh, sa̠ awa ibhinogh eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠ na̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ enyegi iru d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 33 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ e̠ma bho̠ ikokod̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh otu bho̠.  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ a̠d̠izo ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere asu̠nwe̠r bho̠ a̠d̠umeni, sa̠ i̠na a̠zegi ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ asi̠ghe̠gi̠, ya̠ i̠na na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ ma̠ ofugh abar, ezin bho̠ awa e̠mar eloghom ma̠ i̠na. 
\s1 A̠siseiny na̠ o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 4:42-44) 
\p  
\v 35 D̠a̠ ob̠om ame̠ghe̠le̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ esi ola̠ od̠i kukunum a̠siseiny a̠siseiny.  
\v 36 Sa̠ Asai̠mo̠n na̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na bho̠ id̠igh o̠bho̠ro̠gh o̠yo̠.  
\v 37 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh anwa.”  
\v 38 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Id̠ighi ta̠ oten o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ipa̠n a̠risisi, d̠a̠ re̠ma iyed̠i ya̠ itua̠n bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ ami̠ agba ani̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. Ezin bho̠ ami̠ i̠tu̠n o̠ku̠a a̠ru.” \wj* 
\v 39 Sa̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a ma̠ e̠ma a̠ten e̠ma d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh Agalili, agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala d̠awa, sa̠ a̠zegi ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ a̠ruzu a̠nwunom. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh 
\r (Amatiu 8:1-4; A̠luk 5:12-16) 
\p  
\v 40 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh a̠ru ra̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “Wa̠nwuna̠! Ku̠gba ma̠ anwa ta̠ a̠ma̠ra̠, bha̠ koko ami̠ ma̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠.”  
\v 41 Sa̠ igbirigbir o̠ni̠ bho̠ id̠ighi ma̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ i̠na a̠selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kula̠n i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ a̠ma̠ra̠. B̠ab̠ala!”  
\v 42 Sa̠ asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ab̠ab̠ala.  
\v 43 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠ a̠ten a̠yel, sa̠ aghaghana i̠na ma̠a̠:  
\v 44 “Bi̠ghe̠! Ko o̠gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ gi̠e̠ ka̠ a̠leriom ozu d̠oyom ma̠ okur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ozu wa̠ A̠mozizi ato̠ bho̠, ma̠ oleriom ma̠ anwa na̠ a̠d̠um.”  
\v 45 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠na a̠ten agi̠ ka̠ agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ kesi kesi, ma̠ ola̠ o̠du̠ ogir ilologia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ asi̠saragi̠an agi̠ ma̠ egbeiny. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, A̠zizo̠s na̠ opita̠ d̠o̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ebhugh bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na aro̠ghan d̠a̠ etire a̠risisi ya̠ od̠i kukunum. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, a̠nwunom i̠d̠u̠a kesi kesi eru d̠o̠yo̠. 
\c 2  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ Ukula̠ O̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 9:1-8; A̠luk 5:17-26) 
\p  
\v 1 Ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ iten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mula̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m. Sa̠ a̠nwunom i̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠a̠, i̠na od̠i d̠a̠ otu d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ikokod̠ia̠n d̠a̠ otu bho̠ imuzo ma̠ ola̠ e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ otu bho̠ na̠ o̠mara d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ otu bho̠, na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. Sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 3 Sa̠ inya̠ a̠nwunom irol o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠b̠ogina̠ ma̠ obhin ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠yo̠.  
\v 4 Igiel bho̠ awa orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh e̠ti̠ti̠gha od̠igh bho̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠. Sa̠ awa i̠si̠n ibhun d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ i̠kpakpagi̠o̠n imutiom oyol d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu bho̠. Sa̠ i̠wo̠lo̠me̠ni̠ isoroni i̠na d̠a̠ a̠kporokporo bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 5 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa bho̠, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ bho̠, na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠oyom.”  
\v 6 Sa̠ idi ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠, id̠igh i̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ epura̠n d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 7 “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ o̠ni̠ onon na̠ a̠fugh a̠fugh i̠basi̠! A̠nyen ta̠ a̠rue awe̠le̠man i̠karabh ta̠ o̠ni̠, a̠ten A̠zib̠a̠?”  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠loghoma̠n d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an rologi d̠awa, sa̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin?  
\v 9 Oken wa̠ a̠b̠ur a̠pu ma̠ ofugh onigha̠ o̠ni̠ onon wa̠ na̠ a̠b̠ogina̠ bho̠, ‘Na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠oyom,’ bo̠d̠o̠ ofugh ma̠a̠, ‘B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠bhin a̠kporokporo d̠oyom ma̠ a̠rile’?  
\v 10 Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan ma̠a̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠de onon.” Sa̠ i̠na akparame̠ni̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ukula̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠,  
\v 11 \wj “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, b̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠bhin a̠kporokporo d̠oyom ma̠ a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom.” \wj* 
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ a̠bhin a̠kporokporo d̠o̠yo̠ a̠rile d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ eb̠la̠ awa ad̠u̠a, ma̠ ola̠ eb̠la̠ awa ima̠gha̠, sa̠ awa itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “I̠yar ta̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh abar ola̠ o̠ko̠no̠n!” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi ma̠ A̠livai̠ sa̠ //  a̠d̠igh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠d̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n 
\r (Amatiu 9:9-13; A̠luk 5:27-32) 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠mula̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ aka o̠bhi̠i̠y bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ iru d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa.  
\v 14 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh erile bho̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh A̠livai̠, o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ali̠fi̠o̠s ka̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ e̠fe̠m ogun otua̠-ebhugh, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Tu̠o̠no̠me̠ ami̠,” Sa̠ A̠livai̠ a̠b̠etina̠ atu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 15 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ o̠gho̠ na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠livai̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠izo igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh iru ra̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠na na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ id̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠. Sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom iten ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 16 Igiel bho̠ idi ogbo a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠bi̠gh ka̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠ed̠ia̠n id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh na̠ igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ awa ipura̠n ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere, ka̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin na̠ a̠d̠ed̠ia̠n na̠ igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠ka̠rabh bho̠?”  
\v 17 A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠n a̠pura̠n onon, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ogbo ya̠ o̠nwe̠r d̠o̠ i̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ owil, ya̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r bho̠. Ami̠ iru ma̠ ra̠ olebh id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh, ya̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom d̠o̠.” 
\s1 A̠pura̠n ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ one o̠ko̠i̠ 
\r (Amatiu 9:14-17; A̠luk 5:33-39) 
\p  
\v 18 Aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠. Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n na̠ ita̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, ya̠a̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom ine ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠?”  
\v 19 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ogbo erogh bho̠ ta̠ e̠tu̠n ere ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ od̠i na̠ awa bho̠? Yii, awa ko orue d̠o̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, ezin bho̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ od̠i na̠ awa.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ya̠a̠, obhel na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, sa̠ awa ta̠ ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 21 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin o̠go̠go̠ra omom ukpe na̠ ab̠ad̠i̠ ma̠ opupu akapa bo̠. Ezin bho̠, esi wa̠ u̠b̠ad̠i̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠puruna̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ akapa bho̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ agu̠an a̠peleni ma̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 22 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ko o̠lo̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ imom a̠min d̠a̠ opupu akana ozu-e̠nam, bo̠d̠o̠ bha̠ akana ozu-e̠nam bho̠ ta̠ a̠pol, sa̠ a̠min bho̠ ta̠ ezugia̠n ebhe, sa̠ akana bho̠ ta̠ api̠an. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, na̠ o̠lo̠gh imom a̠min d̠a̠ imom rakana ozu-e̠nam.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 12:1-8; A̠luk 6:1-5) 
\p  
\v 23 A̠mite ma̠ ola̠ d̠a̠ odi A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ eten d̠a̠ ari̠si̠ i̠bu̠kpa, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ib̠oghi ma̠ itu i̠bu̠kpa bho̠.  
\v 24 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Nagha! Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ awa na̠ egir abar ola̠ oloko bho̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh bho̠?”  
\v 25 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ abar wa̠ A̠devidi a̠gir igiel bho̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na sekina̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 26 Ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m wa̠ Abi̠ata aro̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ okur bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ abe̠re̠di̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ ya̠ i̠ro̠ inigha̠ ma̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m ma̠ od̠e. Sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ nyen a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na bho̠.”  
\v 27 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Umutiom A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠-epobh bho̠ onigha̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ u̠le̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ o̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ epobh bho̠.  
\v 28 Ezin bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ bha̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠ epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠.” 
\c 3  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ O̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 12:9-14; A̠luk 6:6-11) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mina̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠. Odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ na̠ akpari̠an aro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 2 Idi ogbo d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan e̠kal abar ola̠ odin ob̠ologiom A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ awa ikimeni na̠ egon o̠bi̠gh ku̠gba ma̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠.  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ akpari̠an bho̠ ma̠a̠, “B̠etina̠ ma̠ amara d̠a̠ a̠misigh eb̠la̠ ogbo.”  
\v 4 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ere ma̠ abar wa̠ oloko bho̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ ogir d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠: ogir ib̠eb̠i bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ ogir i̠karabh, otenemeni o̠ni̠ onigha̠ a̠ghud̠um bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ ogigh o̠ni̠?” Ya̠a̠, awa inima̠ i̠ro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m.  
\v 5 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpon eb̠la̠ awa a̠kitineni̠ na̠ ibom i̠gam, ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ e̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠awa bho̠, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom.” Sa̠ i̠na a̠selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ a̠selegha̠n a̠bhon.  
\v 6 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a ka̠ imimia̠n na̠ ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m ta̠ E̠ro̠d\f + \fr 3:6 \fq Ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m ta̠ E̠ro̠d: \ft Awa a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m E̠ro̠d, sa̠ i̠lo̠gh a̠d̠ien A̠zizo̠s, iba̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠damaghan o̠yo̠.\f* igboloma̠ i̠na, ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa ta̠ ebhin egigh i̠na. 
\s1 Ibom ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ aka o̠bhi̠i̠y eko. Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ Agalili na̠ A̠zudia̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 8 Ipa̠n ro̠lo̠gh ya̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, na̠ Idumia̠ na̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan, na̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n. Eb̠la̠ awa iru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n e̠mi̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir bho̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ awa eguri ma̠ oghugh esisa̠n i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠igh, bo̠ka̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ i̠ni̠ro̠m i̠na.  
\v 10 Ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠koko ma̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu asu̠nwe̠r, ma̠ ola̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ ad̠ien kere kere asu̠nwe̠r na̠ ekukurugha̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ka̠ okula̠n o̠yo̠.  
\v 11 Ka̠ obhel ka̠ obhel ola̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ e̠b̠am i̠bi̠gh i̠na, sa̠ awa ta̠ emeleghu d̠a̠ a̠de emulughu d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ efugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na alo̠gh e̠mi̠ ab̠ab̠agi̠na awa ma̠a̠, od̠ighi̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ eloghom i̠na. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s aso̠n d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo-ogir 
\r (Amatiu 10:1-4; A̠luk 6:12-16) 
\p  
\v 13 A̠zizo̠s asi̠n d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu sa̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan oru d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. Sa̠ awa iru.  
\v 14 Sa̠ i̠na aso̠n d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal, a̠ghol awa ma̠ ogbo-ogir d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ ed̠igh na̠ i̠na e̠ro̠, na̠ oruom awa o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ o̠sasaragi̠,  
\v 15 na̠ onigha̠ awa ma̠ a̠limon obhin ozegi i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh o̠si̠ghe̠gi̠.  
\v 16 I̠nye̠n d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo ya̠ i̠na aso̠n bho̠: Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ i̠na a̠ghol A̠pita̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 17 A̠zemsi̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Aze̠bidi, na̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠ Azo̠n (ya̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ghol ma̠ A̠boanazis, wa̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, “anwi̠i̠ny agbararan bho̠”),  
\v 18 na̠ Anduru, na̠ A̠filip, na̠ Abatolomio, na̠ Amatiu, na̠ Ato̠mo̠si̠, na̠ A̠zemsi o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ali̠fi̠o̠s, na̠ Atadi̠o̠s, na̠ Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ ughol a̠d̠ien ma̠ A̠zilo̠t\f + \fr 3:18 \ft A̠zilo̠t: O̠nyi̠ eghun A̠zu ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin onyen ologi na̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ abhe̠l ebhugh d̠awa. \f* bho̠,  
\v 19 na̠ A̠zuda̠s I̠skari̠o̠t, wa̠ ra̠ a̠wol i̠na bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ A̠belzibul 
\r (Amatiu 12:22-32; A̠luk 11:14-23; 12:10) 
\p  
\v 20 Odi obhel A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu wa̠ i̠na na̠ aro̠ghan bho̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ikokod̠ia̠n, ma̠ ola̠ i̠na sekina̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n nyen.  
\v 21 D̠a̠ obhel bho̠ ogbo a̠ghisia̠n ta̠ A̠zizo̠s i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ emite bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ obhin o̠yo̠ o̠d̠u̠a, ezin bho̠ na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, “I̠na bo̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.” 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ ogbo a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m iru ra̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ onon na̠ a̠bhum A̠belzibul, sa̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ A̠belzibul, we̠mu̠ a̠ruru bho̠ na̠ a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠zegi.”  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi awa a̠kokod̠i. Sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “Eru bho̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ a̠ze ma̠ eru asi̠ghe̠? \wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ a̠de e̠ma na̠ aru̠gi̠an na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠, a̠de e̠ma obha̠ ko orue d̠o̠ amara. \wj* 
\v 25 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ eghun otu na̠ aru̠gi̠an na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠, eghun otu obha̠ ko orue d̠o̠ amara. \wj* 
\v 26 \wj Sa̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ Eru bho̠ na̠ aru̠gi̠an na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ko orue d̠o̠ amara; o̠ku̠a bha̠ ita̠ o̠yo̠ na̠ ekunugiom. \wj* 
\v 27 \wj Ya̠a̠ opa̠n agu̠o̠ o̠gba. A̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu omomona̠n ka̠ a̠ghumi ma̠ i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, a̠sigimeni ka̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ abhad̠i̠ ma̠ omomona̠n bho̠? I̠se̠ kisa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue afo̠i̠ny otu d̠o̠yo̠. \wj* 
\v 28 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, i̠karabh ka̠ i̠karabh ya̠ o̠ni̠ a̠gir, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ ya̠ o̠ni̠ a̠fugh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man. \wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ko o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠. Ezin bho̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠sor oloko ogir i̠karabh ola̠ ta̠ aro̠ kid̠ud̠ul.” \wj* 
\v 30 A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠nigha̠ awa, ezin bho̠ awa na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠gir ogir d̠o̠yo̠. 
\s1 Onweni na̠ A̠rumor ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 12:46-50; A̠luk 8:19-21) 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ onweni na̠ a̠rumor ta̠ A̠zizo̠s iru ra̠ i̠mara d̠a̠ etire. Sa̠ awa iruom a̠duom odi o̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠gba onigha̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠na a̠ru ra̠ abi̠ghan awa.  
\v 32 Ya̠a̠, o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom na̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de eko i̠na, sa̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, onweni d̠oyom na̠ a̠rumor d̠oyom od̠i d̠a̠ etire na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠bi̠ghan oyom.  
\v 33 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj “Onweni d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠rumor d̠ami̠ ka̠ wa̠ a̠nyen?” \wj* 
\v 34 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpon awa ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de bho̠ a̠kitineni, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ikpone, i̠nye̠n onweni d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠rumor d̠ami̠. \wj* 
\v 35 \wj Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠gir agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ato̠ bho̠, bha̠ umor d̠ami̠, na̠ u̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, na̠ onweni d̠ami̠.”\wj* 
\c 4  
\s1 A̠sidogh Ogbebh ma̠ Ed̠ia̠n bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 13:1-9; A̠luk 8:4-8) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠puta̠ ake̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ aka o̠bhi̠i̠y eko. Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom isor esi bho̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y eko bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ egbolom.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin ra̠sidogh atu̠ghu̠me̠ni awa ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar agba ma̠a̠:  
\v 3 \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha o! Ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n agi̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ ogbebh ed̠ia̠n.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Sa̠ a̠mite ma̠ ola̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠kpo ma̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠ asar bho̠, sa̠ idi ikpo imel d̠a̠ eten, sa̠ i̠nu̠r iru ra̠ ikpokpoiny id̠e i̠mado̠n.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Ya̠a̠, idi ikpo sa̠ imel d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbe̠o̠ma, esi ola̠ o̠do̠gho̠l bho̠ okud̠um d̠o̠. Sa̠ awa i̠rabh epa̠ ma̠ o̠su̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠do̠gho̠l bho̠ okud̠um d̠o̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠ igiel ogogo a̠mite bho̠, sa̠ i̠nyu̠n i̠ghaghara d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ osi d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠ka bho̠. \wj* 
\v 7 \wj Sa̠ idi ikpo imel d̠a̠ e̠ko̠ko̠ ib̠ub̠ulom, sa̠ ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠ i̠su̠ ikpegiom ed̠ia̠n bho̠ i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠, ma̠ ola̠ awa o̠su̠ d̠o̠ emum itu. \wj* 
\p  
\v 8 \wj “Ya̠a̠, idi ikpo bho̠ imel d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠de, sa̠ i̠su̠ imite, imum a̠d̠izo itu. Idi imum a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh (30) a̠bin ya̠ ubhin ugbebh bho̠, idi e̠rabharabh (60) a̠bin, idi i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100) a̠bin.”\wj* 
\v 9 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to, anagha o!” \wj* 
\s1 Ezin wa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rughom ra̠sidogh bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 13:10-17; A̠luk 8:9-10) 
\p  
\v 10 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ A̠zizo̠s ku̠ku̠m odi ma̠ esi, sa̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo ogir bho̠, na̠ ipa̠n ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠, ipura̠n i̠na ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ra̠sidogh bho̠. 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “D̠a̠ inyin bha̠, na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ologhom i̠di̠ar e̠wo̠gi̠na irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Ya̠a̠, ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠inyin bho̠, kabar kabar bha̠ awa ta̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n d̠a̠ a̠sidogh.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a,\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘awa ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ okpon okpon,\wj* 
\q2 \wj ya̠a̠ awa ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠,\wj* 
\q1 \wj ta̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n\wj* 
\q2 \wj ya̠a̠ awa ko o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠.\wj* 
\q1 \wj B̠o̠ka̠ awa itiba̠ra̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠awa!’\wj*\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Azaya 6:9-10\x*\wj ” \wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠ ezin A̠sidogh Ogbebh ma̠ Ed̠ia̠n bho̠ 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin u̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ ezin a̠sidogh onon ke̠re̠? O̠ku̠a ka̠ inyin ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan eb̠la̠ ra̠sidogh? \wj* 
\v 14 \wj Ogbebhma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠ a̠gbebh ikpo a̠fugh bho̠. \wj* 
\v 15 \wj Ikpo ya̠ imel d̠a̠ eten bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠, agu̠o̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ Eru bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ asi̠ghe̠gi̠ ma̠ ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa. \wj* 
\v 16 \wj Ya̠a̠, ikpo ya̠ imel d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ ibhin d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi i̠da ibhin. \wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ya̠a̠, isi d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠ka, sa̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ekud̠i obhel. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ali̠gam a̠ruzu na̠ ad̠agi̠an ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ awa ku̠ku̠m, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ikpo a̠fugh bho̠, sa̠ imel i̠d̠u̠a.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ imel d̠a̠ ed̠um ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh bho̠, \wj* 
\v 19 \wj ya̠a̠ a̠tepa̠ sa̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh e̠mara̠nwunom, e̠li̠la na̠ e̠me̠me̠m e̠mara̠nwunom i̠su̠ i̠mi̠no̠m ma̠ ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ ma̠ ola̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ omum itu.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ya̠a̠, ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ imel d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠de bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ sa̠ i̠da ibhin, sa̠ imum itu: idi a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh (30), idi e̠rabharabh (60), idi i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100), d̠a̠ ikpo ya̠ ubhin ugbebh bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ato̠di̠ Bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 8:16-18) 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ asu̠o̠m ato̠di̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠bhin abafu̠ a̠kpegiom bo̠d̠o̠ ta̠ oguri d̠a̠ ekpukpu akpata od̠i ke̠re̠? I̠na ko o̠gbam d̠o̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ esi ola̠ a̠sora̠n ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Abar ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ola̠ ko omutiom d̠o̠ bo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ abar ola̠ u̠wo̠gi̠ ola̠ ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ obhin omutiom oyol bo̠.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to, amar amu̠gho̠n o!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mina̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ibhine ma̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠ ma̠ e̠tu̠o̠m abar. A̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ inyin ibhin u̠tu̠o̠m abar bho̠ bha̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ inyin ta̠ obhin o̠mu̠gho̠nyan, sa̠ ta̠ o̠lo̠gho̠m o̠gbam.\wj*\f + \fr 4:24 \ft Agu̠o̠ inyin ubhin u̠to̠ bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ obhin o̠to̠ onigha̠ inyin nyen.\f* 
\v 25 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ ate̠i̠ ya̠ ib̠ui ta̠ o̠lo̠gho̠m o̠gbam. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ ate̠i̠ i̠ki̠kara, iya̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ bho̠ eka̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠r obhin.” \wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ na̠ e̠su̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bha̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ola̠ a̠kpo ma̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n sa̠ asar d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠. \wj* 
\v 27 \wj A̠d̠igh a̠d̠uga̠la̠n, bo̠d̠o̠ etita̠n, ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠ na̠ a̠kod̠u na̠ asu̠ma, ya̠a̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠ na̠ e̠mu̠r na̠ e̠su̠ na̠ emite. Ya̠a̠, i̠na na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠ na̠ ebhin na̠ e̠su̠. \wj* 
\v 28 \wj A̠de bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ ekpo ed̠ia̠n na̠ asu̠ na̠ a̠mum otu; ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠pol a̠mutiom i̠mu̠nu̠mu̠n, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom egum, ka̠ a̠tepa̠ sa̠ ta̠ a̠mum otu ola̠ ta̠ amar akpo̠.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Otu o̠bu̠kpa bho̠ ma̠ o̠kpo̠ ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠ ta̠ a̠b̠ogh, ezin bho̠ obhel ib̠ua̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠lei.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ekpo Amu̠stad bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 13:31-32; A̠luk 13:18-19) 
\p  
\v 30 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ ta̠ obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ere? Bo̠d̠o̠, ka̠ i̠yar ta̠ obhin a̠kere a̠sidogh o̠tu̠o̠m?\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Agu̠b̠an ekpo amu̠stad\wj*\f + \fr 4:31 \fq Ekpo Amu̠stad: \ft Ekpo ola̠ aki̠r opa̠n d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l; od̠i ka̠ ekpo obom o̠nyi̠ o̠kai̠ ola̠, ka̠ ugbebh sa̠ na̠ asu̠ na̠ a̠ten oriren.\f*\wj ola̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin a̠gbebh d̠a̠ a̠lei, ya̠a̠ ekpo bho̠ aki̠r a̠pu ma̠ eb̠la̠ ipa̠n ikpo ed̠ia̠n,\wj* 
\v 32 \wj sa̠ asu̠ a̠mite a̠ten obom oriren wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ i̠gha, sa̠ i̠nu̠r iru ra̠ ilo ma̠ a̠rutu d̠a̠ i̠gha bho̠.”\wj* 
\v 33 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠d̠izo a̠sidogh ya̠ o̠ku̠a, a̠bhin atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ awa ta̠ erue e̠mu̠gho̠nyan.  
\v 34 I̠na na̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ abar a̠nigha̠ awa, ma̠ ola̠ i̠na obhin d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠sidogh agba. Ya̠a̠, igiel i̠na sekina̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ku̠ku̠m od̠i, sa̠ i̠na na̠ amar na̠ agba kabar kabar na̠ asi̠si̠ghe̠ni̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠kimeni ma̠ ebiri 
\r (Amatiu 8:23-27; A̠luk 8:23-27) 
\p  
\v 35 A̠dule a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Id̠ighi ta̠ o̠b̠e̠i̠y d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y eko bho̠.” \wj* 
\v 36 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠we̠le̠man o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ka̠ id̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh wa̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠i bho̠, sa̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠b̠e̠i̠y. Sa̠, idi ipa̠n a̠rughugh i̠gbo̠gbu̠an awa i̠gi̠.  
\v 37 Sa̠ obom ebiri a̠sor d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y-eko bho̠, sa̠ abadi̠ bho̠ agam ma̠ ola̠ amu̠m ipoka̠n id̠igh na̠ emuzo d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠ ma̠ owiyom.  
\v 38 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s amanaghan d̠a̠ agba eti oghugh bho̠ agbam e̠mu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ob̠enegioma̠ e̠mu̠, sa̠ ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ a̠kod̠u. 
\p Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠su̠me̠ni̠ i̠na ifugh ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, a̠d̠ugh wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin i̠yar bho̠, na̠ ogboloma̠ d̠o̠ nyam ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠etina̠ ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ ebiri bho̠ ma̠a̠ \wj “Kima̠!” \wj* Sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ abadi̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “B̠okume!” \wj* Sa̠ ebiri bho̠ a̠kima̠, sa̠ abadi̠ bho̠ a̠b̠okum, sa̠ ekima̠ a̠mite.  
\v 40 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ere ka̠ inyin na̠ oghil a̠rugugu? Ere wa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠?” \wj* 
\p  
\v 41 Sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa ma̠ ibom, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠pura̠n odi ma̠a̠, “Onon ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠, ma̠ ola̠ ebiri na̠ abadi̠ eka̠ na̠ e̠nagha i̠na?” 
\c 5  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ozu odi o̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 8:28-34; A̠luk 8:26-39) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠b̠e̠i̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y eko Agalili d̠a̠ agba ebhugh Age̠rasa.  
\v 2 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠sor d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh na̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ a̠bia̠, ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠karabh esi bho̠ ra̠ ami̠nana i̠na.  
\v 3 O̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ o̠karabh esi, ya̠a̠ bebina̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠rue ma̠ o̠bhad̠i̠ o̠yo̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, ubhin eka̠ ma̠ i̠go̠ro̠go̠ro̠ o̠bhad̠i̠ i̠na isibhom d̠o̠ eguri ma̠ onin esi nyen.  
\v 4 A̠d̠izo igiel, ubhin gha̠n i̠go̠ro̠go̠ro̠ na̠ ikoli o̠du̠o̠m i̠na d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ na̠ a̠sike oguri ma̠ esi, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠gbugbo gha̠n i̠go̠ro̠go̠ro̠ na̠ ikoli ya̠ ubhin u̠du̠o̠m i̠na bho̠, sa̠ a̠nwinigi gha̠n ikpo a̠rukurogh ya̠ ubhin u̠du̠o̠m a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ nyen. Sa̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ igba̠ ya̠ obhin osibh o̠yo̠ oguri onin esi na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 5 A̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n a̠d̠io i̠na na̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ o̠karabh esi na̠ d̠a̠ ranyu̠ od̠i na̠ d̠a̠ a̠rugugum, na̠ a̠mulughu na̠ a̠bhin i̠pad̠i̠ i̠gbaki̠ghe̠ na̠ a̠guyogh ozu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh A̠zizo̠s ma̠ esi egbeiny bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ghil ka̠ a̠mel a̠kpud̠ia̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠na.  
\v 7 Sa̠ a̠bhin obom okoroko a̠mulughu a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ ami̠ ka̠ odi a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ere a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ odi? A̠zizo̠s, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠. Ami̠ na̠ a̠siseiny anwa d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ko ogbikimeni ami̠!”  
\v 8 Ezin bho̠ bha̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠karabh e̠mu̠gh mite ma̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠ onon.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠d̠ien d̠oyom ka̠ ubhelegi eka̠?” \wj* 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “A̠d̠izo,” ezin bho̠ i̠yar a̠b̠utu. 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na akparame̠ni̠ ale̠gh A̠zizo̠s ma̠ i̠na oze d̠o̠ awa asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh obha̠. 
\p  
\v 11 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, obom o̠lo̠gh roporopo i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ eb̠ub̠um a̠de d̠a̠ aka esi bho̠, na̠ eb̠u na̠ ed̠e. 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ruome i̠yar o̠gi̠ ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ruzu roporopo bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ma̠ra̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ imite ka̠ id̠igh d̠a̠ roporopo bho̠. Roporopo bho̠ ta̠ elei agu̠o̠ o̠gho̠ o̠ni̠r (2,000), sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ eb̠ub̠um a̠de bho̠ ighil isor d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y-eko bho̠, i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠an imugughu. 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekponom roporopo bho̠ ighil ka̠ i̠gba d̠a̠ ibom na̠ i̠gbara re̠ma bho̠, ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠. Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ imite iru ra̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠.  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ awa iru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ ka̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de, na̠ a̠loghoma̠n ozu, a̠bura̠ ma̠ ibura̠, sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa.  
\v 16 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, i̠gba ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠um, sekina̠ iya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ roporopo bho̠.  
\v 17 Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠le̠gh A̠zizo̠s ma̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ebhugh d̠awa.  
\v 18 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ a̠puru ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Ma̠ra̠ ami̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m anwa.”  
\v 19 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Mula̠ ma̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom, ma̠ ka̠ agba ma̠ a̠mutiom ibom i̠di̠ar ya̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ nyam bho̠, na̠ okpon igbirigbir ya̠ i̠na a̠leriom anwa bho̠.” \wj* 
\v 20 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠ten agi̠ ka̠ agba asasaragi̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh A̠d̠iobh Re̠ma bho̠, ma̠ ibom i̠di̠ar ya̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠gir a̠nigha̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠eton odi o̠nyani̠ d̠a̠ omugh  //  sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ ani̠ ola̠ asi̠ i̠gbo̠ d̠a̠ ozu 
\r (Amatiu 9:18-26; A̠luk 8:40-56) 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠puta̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh ab̠e̠i̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ikokod̠ia̠n iru d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ aka o̠bhi̠i̠y eko bho̠.  
\v 22 Sa̠ odi we̠mu̠ okponom ma̠ otu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Azari̠o̠s a̠ru ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠. Igiel bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠,  
\v 23 ale̠gh i̠na akparame̠ni̠ agba ma̠a̠, “O̠gbara o̠nyani̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ ra̠ omugh. Siseiny, tue ra̠ agbam agu̠o̠ d̠oyom d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠koko i̠na ma̠ a̠d̠umeni.”  
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh na̠ i̠na agi̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s iko i̠na ikiton.  
\v 25 Odi ani̠ ola̠ asi̠ na̠ e̠gbo̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ ma̠ a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) ala aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 26 I̠na na̠ a̠gbika̠ ma̠ ibom d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ a̠d̠izo a̠riwil, a̠robh eb̠la̠ ikpoki d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ okokua̠n, ya̠a̠ esi bho̠ aro̠ ku ma̠ opu opu.  
\v 27 Igiel bho̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n iya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠kukurugha̠n d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠, awo̠l d̠a̠ aman ta̠ A̠zizo̠s ka̠ a̠kula̠n ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 28 Ezin bho̠, i̠na a̠ma̠ra̠ d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠kula̠n ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ku̠ku̠m eka̠, bha̠ ami̠ od̠um.”  
\v 29 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ asi̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠gbo̠ bho̠ isobha̠n, sa̠ i̠na a̠loghoma̠n ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠um d̠a̠ asu̠nwe̠r bho̠.  
\v 30 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghoma̠n ma̠a̠ a̠limon na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ adama ma̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠nyen a̠kula̠n ibura̠ d̠ami̠?” \wj* 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ abi̠gh agu̠o̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom na̠ e̠ni̠ran eko nyam ekiton, sa̠ anwa na̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj ‘A̠nyen a̠kula̠n ami̠?’\wj*”  
\v 32 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠kpon d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ a̠kitineni ma̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠kula̠n i̠na bho̠.  
\v 33 Igiel bho̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠loghoma̠n abar wa̠ na̠ a̠mutuma̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠rugugu, a̠bhin igiri a̠ru ra̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠bhin ya̠gia̠ga̠i agba ma̠ eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ abar bho̠ a̠mite a̠nigha̠ i̠na.  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠nyani̠ bho̠, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠koko nyam. Gi̠e̠ na̠ ekima̠ ma̠ a̠miza̠n d̠a̠ egbika̠ d̠oyom.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 35 A̠zizo̠s od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ agba ma̠ i̠nye̠n, sa̠ idi a̠nwunom i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Azari̠o̠s ra̠ i̠gba i̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ekpo epobh o̠nyani̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠sobha̠n! Ko onyegi mu ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 36 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhogia̠n asu̠gbagba d̠awa, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ u̠gala A̠zu bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Ko oghil a̠rugugu, ma̠ra̠ ka̠ a̠ma̠ra̠.”\wj* 
\v 37 I̠na na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m o̠yo̠, a̠ten A̠puta̠, na̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n umor ta̠ A̠zemsi.  
\v 38 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ we̠mu̠ otu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh ka̠ a̠nwunom od̠i d̠a̠ asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an, sa̠ na̠ emulughu na̠ eleghe na̠ e̠gba ma̠ igbir.  
\v 39 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi otu bho̠, sa̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ odin ere na̠ o̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an, na̠ oleghe ma̠ o̠ku̠a? O̠nyani̠ bho̠ ta̠ omugh d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ na̠ a̠kod̠u ma̠ adala.” \wj* 
\v 40 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠mo̠lo̠gh i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na. Ya̠a̠, i̠na a̠ze awa a̠mutiom, sa̠ a̠bhin onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na bho̠, a̠d̠igh agi̠ d̠a̠ esi wa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ aro̠ bho̠.  
\v 41 Sa̠ i̠na a̠sibh o̠nyani̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Talita, Kumi!” \wj* wa̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠gbara o̠nyani̠, b̠etina̠!”\wj* 
\v 42 Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠ ake̠ ma̠ orile (i̠na d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ala). Sa̠ abar bho̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ ibom.  
\v 43 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠bukiom awa ma̠a̠ awa o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ a̠mite bho̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ o̠ni̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ abar ta̠ a̠d̠e.” \wj* 
\c 6  
\s1 A̠nwunom e̠ma ta̠ A̠zizo̠s ighel i̠na 
\r (Amatiu 13:53-58; A̠luk 4:16-30) 
\p  
\v 1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ Ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠ten e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma wa̠ i̠na a̠mite bho̠.  
\v 2 Ate̠i̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ otu u̠gala bho̠. Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n a̠d̠izo ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠na bho̠. 
\p Sa̠ awa ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “I̠na ate̠i̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n d̠a̠ a̠ken? I̠nye̠n ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien eloghom abar ya̠ unigha̠ i̠na bho̠? Ma̠ ola̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir ibom ilologia̠n ya̠ o̠ko̠no̠n?  
\v 3 Onon o̠du̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠meri bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? Umor ta̠ A̠zemsi̠ na̠ A̠zosisi na̠ A̠zud na̠ Asai̠mo̠n d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? Aru̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bo̠ na̠ i̠yar i̠se̠n ke̠re̠?” Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ awa ighel i̠na. 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Esi ola̠ owil olei d̠o̠ ma̠ abar bo̠, a̠ten d̠a̠ e̠ma wa̠ i̠na a̠mite bho̠, sekina̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ogbo a̠ghisia̠n, na̠ d̠a̠ eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠.” \wj* 
\v 5 I̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir bebina̠ onin ilologia̠n i̠se̠, a̠ten o̠gbamagi̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ a̠ruzu i̠ki̠kara a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠, okoko awa od̠umeni.  
\v 6 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh i̠na ma̠ ilologia̠n ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom a̠duom d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 10:5-15; A̠luk 9:1-6) 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ eghighira̠ bho̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom. 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠, sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠ ob̠etina̠ erile, i̠wal o̠ni̠ ma̠ ebu, a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ a̠limon ya̠ obhin oze i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh,  
\v 8 sa̠ akparame̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ko obhin bebina̠ abar ma̠ eb̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, a̠ten okpeti. Ed̠ia̠n o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, e̠kpa o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, okpoki o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ro̠kara ikpoki d̠inyin nyen. \wj* 
\v 9 \wj I̠lo̠gi̠ane̠ ma̠ ragbaka, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ko obhin akapa onwegina̠.” \wj* 
\v 10 \wj Igiel inyin ud̠igh d̠a̠ otu-esul, i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ tu̠tu̠n inyin ta̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠. \wj* 
\v 11 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ inyin u̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma ola̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ o̠da d̠o̠ inyin ebhin, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ inyin, bha̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ ma̠ ekpukpu ma̠ ibhugh bho̠ ma̠ e̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ re̠b̠ab̠a a̠sike d̠inyin. Obha̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh ebhum ase̠ a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 12 Sa̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠gba imutiom ma̠ a̠nwunom etiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh.  
\v 13 Awa ize ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh sa̠ izugioghom a̠d̠izo ogbo asu̠nwe̠r ma̠ amu̠nu̠, ikoko awa id̠umeni. 
\s1 E̠ro̠d a̠gigh Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 14:1-12; A̠luk 9:7-9) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ o̠du̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s asi̠saragi̠an ate̠i̠ kesikesi, ma̠ ola̠ O̠li̠le̠ma E̠ro̠d amu̠gho̠n a̠gboloma̠ i̠na. Idi ogbo i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠, i̠na Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um, bha̠ ezin bho̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ a̠limon ya̠ obhin ogir ilologia̠n bho̠.  
\v 15 Ipa̠n ogbo sa̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “I̠na I̠lai̠za.” Ipa̠n sa̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “I̠na odi owil wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ igied̠i bho̠.”  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ E̠ro̠d amu̠gho̠n a̠gboloma̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, “Azo̠n wa̠ ami̠ isobh e̠mu̠ igigh bho̠ na̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um.”  
\v 17 E̠ro̠d na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠bhin i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠ruom a̠nwunom ob̠ol Azo̠n, o̠bhad̠i̠ o̠yo̠ od̠ighom ikoli, ma̠ ebula̠ E̠ro̠di̠as ani̠ ta̠ A̠filip umor d̠o̠yo̠, wa̠ i̠na E̠ro̠d akpakpa a̠bhin bho̠.  
\v 18 Azo̠n aro̠ ma̠ o̠gba o̠gba onigha̠ E̠ro̠d ma̠a̠, “Na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ nyam o̠kpakpa ani̠ umor d̠oyom obhi̠n.”  
\v 19 E̠ro̠di̠as a̠din o̠ku̠a a̠gurumeni ma̠ ologi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Azo̠n sa̠ abho̠ro̠gh ogigh o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠.  
\v 20 E̠ro̠d a̠ghila̠n Azo̠n sa̠ a̠kponom i̠na, ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠loghom ma̠a̠ Azo̠n o̠ni̠ igielake̠ sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. A̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar ya̠ Azo̠n agba bho̠ e̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠ ma̠ ologi ta̠ E̠ro̠d, ku̠ku̠m eka̠, i̠na a̠ba̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠nagha asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 21 Ekunuguma̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠sora̠n a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ola̠ E̠ro̠d a̠soroni ma̠ o̠d̠e̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ irileghom ebhugh bho̠, na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ e̠gham, na̠ ogbo ya̠ ilei abar d̠a̠ Agalili, ma̠ o̠ghe̠re̠ghu̠o̠m a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ u̠mar i̠na bho̠.  
\v 22 Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ ta̠ E̠ro̠di̠as a̠d̠igh a̠ru ra̠ aghe̠r i̠gba d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠gba bho̠ id̠igh ologi ma̠ E̠ro̠d na̠ ogbo ya̠ isor d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ E̠ro̠d agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠gbara o̠nyani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Puru ami̠ ma̠ abar na̠ abar ola̠ na̠ ebhir anwa ma̠ o̠te̠i̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam.”  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠ia̠n i̠zo̠ a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠ “Kabar kabar ola̠ anwa ipuru, ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam, aro̠ ku̠ ma̠ atu̠gi̠an irileghom d̠ami̠ eka̠.”  
\v 24 Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ ad̠u̠a agi̠ ka̠ a̠pura̠n onweni d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ipuru ma̠ ere?” Sa̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “E̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠,”  
\v 25 Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ a̠nugia̠n ka̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ O̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh anwa ma̠ onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n epa̠ ma̠ e̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠kpa imobh”  
\v 26 Sa̠ E̠ro̠d a̠kpon igbirigbir ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ibom, ku̠ku̠m eka̠ i̠na na̠ one d̠o̠ ma̠ ogineni o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ ri̠zo̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠d̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ isor d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠.  
\v 27 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom epa̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠kponom i̠na bho̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ otu ikoli bho̠ ka̠ osobh e̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n. Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠sobh e̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n,  
\v 28 sa̠ i̠na alo̠gh e̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n d̠a̠ e̠kpa imobh bho̠ a̠bhin a̠ruom o̠nyani̠ bho̠, sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ a̠bhin agi̠o̠m onweni d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 29 Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n i̠mu̠gho̠n abar bho̠, sa̠ awa iru ra̠ ibhin eputa̠ ozu bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ id̠i. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n  //  d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala o̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 14:13-21; A̠luk 9:10-17; Azo̠n 6:1-14) 
\p  
\v 30 Sa̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ imula̠ iru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s ra̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa igir bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ awa ubhin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 31 Sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom idi na̠ eru, idi na̠ e̠gi̠, ma̠ ola̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ bebina̠ e̠ti̠ti̠gha obhel ola̠ od̠e abar. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Itue oten o̠gi̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ i̠yar ku̠ku̠m ta̠ o̠ro̠, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin osira̠ ma̠ epobh ekud̠i obhel.”  
\v 32 Sa̠ awa id̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh iten i̠gi̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ awa ku̠ku̠m ta̠ e̠ro̠.  
\v 33 Ya̠a̠, a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom e̠bi̠gh igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠ sa̠ i̠wal iloghom esi bho̠ awa na̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠. Sa̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠ma bho̠, ikpo ma̠ eghil i̠wo̠l ya̠ a̠wel ka̠ id̠ia̠ imisi ma̠ esi bho̠.  
\v 34 Igiel bho̠ awa isul bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pel a̠bhun, abi̠gh obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom, sa̠ igbirigbir a̠nwunom bho̠ id̠ighi i̠na, ezin bho̠ awa i̠gu̠b̠an ro̠nana ya̠ o̠ni̠ okponom o̠to̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin obhel atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar.  
\v 35 Igiel bho̠ a̠d̠io na̠ ate̠i̠ a̠dule bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Onon esi ola̠ od̠i kukunum, ya̠a̠ obhel bho̠ na̠ a̠ten.  
\v 36 Ruome ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ eten e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠sala ari̠si̠ na̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma ya̠ itua̠n bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ awa e̠bho̠ro̠gh abar egho ed̠e.”  
\v 37 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ inigha̠ awa ma̠ abar ed̠e.” \wj* Sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a bha̠ i̠yar obhin ikpoki ya̠ ta̠ elei agu̠o̠ ogho e̠wala (200) a̠dinari̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ ogho ma̠ abe̠re̠di̠ onigha̠ awa ma̠ od̠e ke̠re̠?”  
\v 38 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin unwuna̠ ma̠ i̠ni̠ ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠? I̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ ekpon.” \wj* Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ ikpon sa̠ iru ra̠ i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠yar unwuna̠ ogho ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ na̠ i̠wal ikpo ina̠.”  
\v 39 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ e̠gba enigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ i̠gho̠gho̠ bho̠ ma̠ ebu ebu.  
\v 40 Sa̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ rebu i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100) na̠ eruba̠l na̠ d̠iobh (50) o̠ni̠.  
\v 41 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin ogho ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ bho̠ na̠ i̠wal ikpo ina̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠tutumeni ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠puinyogh ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ bho̠ na̠ ina̠ bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠ru̠gi̠ onigha̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠.  
\v 42 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa id̠e ilegha̠n,  
\v 43 sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ikokod̠i ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r abe̠re̠di̠ na̠ ina̠ ya̠ isugho bho̠, sa̠ imuzo ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) a̠rukpuom.  
\v 44 O̠nu̠ ilobhiri a̠nwunom ya̠ id̠e ani̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠, ilei d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala (5,000). 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠rile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m 
\r (Amatiu 14:22-33; Azo̠n 6:15-21) 
\p  
\v 45 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠nugi ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh od̠ia̠ ob̠etina̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠tsai̠da d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y eko bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na ta̠ aro̠ a̠ruom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ oyeleghu.  
\v 46 Igiel bho̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ eyeleghu bho̠, sa̠ i̠na asi̠n igu ka̠ a̠d̠igh a̠siseiny.  
\v 47 D̠a̠ a̠dule a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, ma̠ igiel ola̠ oghugh bho̠ na̠ a̠misi d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io o̠bhi̠i̠y eko bho̠, bha̠ A̠zizo̠s ku̠ku̠m od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ egbolom.  
\v 48 Sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh ka̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠gbaghala ma̠ i̠d̠o̠m, ezin bho̠ awa i̠zo̠ghu̠ na̠ e̠dama ma̠ okukugh bho̠. D̠a̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ awa, sa̠ a̠ru ra̠ orile oten.  
\v 49 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ awa i̠bi̠gh ka̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠ awa na̠ e̠bi̠gh egua̠de, sa̠ awa ikpogion izul imulughu.  
\v 50 A̠rugugu isibh ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s anu̠r agba a̠nigha awa ma̠a̠, “I̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin! Ami̠-o! O̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu!”  
\v 51 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh wa̠ awa od̠i bho̠, sa̠ okukugh bho̠ a̠kugh a̠kunugiom. Sa̠ id̠igh ilologia̠n ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ma̠ ibom,  
\v 52 ezin bho̠ awa ta̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ obhin ogir ilologia̠n wa̠ ina̠ a̠b̠uyumeni ma̠ abe̠re̠di̠ bho̠, o̠mu̠gho̠nyan e̠mi̠ a̠limon ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ ogbo asu̠nwe̠r d̠a̠ Age̠ne̠sare̠t 
\r (Amatiu 14:34-36) 
\p  
\v 53 I̠nye̠n iten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠b̠e̠i̠ ka̠ isul d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠, d̠a̠ Age̠ne̠sare̠t.  
\v 54 Igiel bho̠ awa ipel ibhun d̠a̠ egbolom bho̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom ilelegi epa̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 55 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ighil igir eb̠la̠ ebhugh bho̠ ka̠ i̠gba inigha̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo. Sa̠ a̠nwunom irod̠i d̠a̠ ra̠kporokporo ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na kesikesi ola̠ i̠na a̠misi.  
\v 56 Kesikesi ola̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠misi, a̠d̠igh o̠gbara e̠ma, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ obom e̠ma, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ re̠sala ari̠si̠, a̠nwunom ibhin ogbo asu̠nwe̠r e̠gi̠ ka̠ e̠te̠i̠ i̠na d̠a̠ regbolom a̠b̠ua̠, ma̠ i̠na ma̠ okoko. Sa̠ awa i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠ oma̠ra̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogbo asu̠nwe̠r bho̠ ta̠ ekula̠n bebina̠ akapa anyu̠ d̠o̠yo̠, d̠a̠ esi bho̠ u̠labh bho̠. Sa̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ ikula̠n i̠na bho̠ id̠um. 
\c 7  
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni I̠to̠to̠gi Ikei bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 15:1-9) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ idi i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m iru ra̠ ikokod̠ia̠n sa̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na.  
\v 2 Sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh ma̠, idi ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ibhin aru̠gu̠o̠ ya̠ o̠b̠ab̠ala d̠o̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, o̠ku̠a bha̠ awa ititila̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ kisa̠ na̠ ed̠e.  
\v 3 Ya̠a̠, Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo A̠zu bho̠ id̠egha̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ku̠gba ma̠ awa i̠mar d̠o̠ etitila̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa. Awa na̠ esibhom i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ d̠awa.  
\v 4 Ka̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ esi a̠b̠ua̠ iru, ka̠ awa otitila̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ egirghan bho̠, awa id̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n. Sa̠ isibhom ipa̠n a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar iya̠ awa i̠tu̠ghan d̠a̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ bho̠, iya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠: otitol rokpa̠ko amu̠m, oloko amu̠m, ra̠sugh e̠ko̠lo̠gho̠l amu̠m. 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ezin kere ma̠ ola̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom o̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ bho̠, sa̠ na̠ ebhin aru̠gu̠o̠ ya̠ o̠b̠ab̠ala d̠o̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n?” 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Azaya a̠wa̠ ga̠i a̠gboloma̠ inyin, ma̠ inyin ribhelebhel, ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ uguri bho̠ ma̠a̠,\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘A̠nwunom i̠nye̠n na̠ ebhin aru̠nu̠ d̠awa na̠ edoni ami̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj ya̠a̠ rologi d̠awa esigima̠ ami̠.\wj* 
\q1  
\v 7 \wj Awa na̠ e̠ko̠l ami̠ ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ iya̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠.’\wj*\f + \fr 7:7 \ft \xt Azaya 29:13\f* 
\m  
\v 8 \wj Inyin ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ oloko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ o̠tu̠o̠m abar, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m ku ma̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ta̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ i̠na ab̠aram agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin o̠mar ologhom agu̠o̠ oguri roloko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ aka, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin omutiom ita̠ inyin.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj A̠mozizi agba ma̠a̠, izuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin, sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ onweni bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bha̠ ogigh. \wj* 
\v 11 \wj Ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ ogba ma̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ oweni bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Kere kere e̠ne̠ghe̠ ola̠ inyin ka̠ u̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠,’ \wj* 
\v 12 \wj inyin uma̠ra̠ mu ma̠ awa egir abar enigha̠ ma̠ onweni bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠awa.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Inyin na̠ orughom ikpo a̠fugh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wokuma̠ a̠limon bo̠, ma̠ ola̠ inyin na̠ obhin i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠inyin na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny o̠gu̠man bho̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ ogir a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar iya̠ i̠gu̠b̠an o̠ku̠a.”\wj* 
\s1 O̠kpo̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 15:10-20) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ a̠mula̠ a̠kokod̠i ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha ami̠, kere kere o̠ni̠, ma̠a̠ e̠mu̠gho̠nyan.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Abar ola̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ etire na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ozu o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ d̠o̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ iya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ emite bho̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠. \wj* 
\v 16 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to, amar amu̠gho̠n o!”\wj*\f + \fr 7:16 \ft Idi igba̠iny a̠d̠ire bho̠ i̠lo̠gh i̠se̠n iya̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ 4:23.\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ipura̠n i̠na igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠sidogh bho̠.  
\v 18 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin u̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ nyen ke̠re̠? I̠mu̠gho̠nyane̠ ma̠a̠, kabar kabar ola̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ etire na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠ d̠o̠, ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue api̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠? \wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ezin bho̠ na̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ekpo ologi bho̠, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ okurogh, sa̠ na̠ a̠ten ati̠n na̠ a̠mite na̠ ad̠u̠a.”\wj* (O̠ku̠a bha̠, A̠zizo̠s agba a̠soroni ma̠a̠, eb̠la̠ ed̠ia̠n e̠b̠ab̠ala.)  
\v 20 Sa̠ agba alo̠gho̠m ma̠a̠: \wj “Abar wa̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠mite bho̠, bha̠ wa̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ezin bho̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi bho̠, d̠a̠ ekpo ologi o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ emite: i̠karabh i̠ru̠ru̠an, ari̠gi̠, a̠b̠igh, ogigh o̠ni̠,\wj* 
\v 22 \wj od̠e e̠ma d̠a̠ ilom, o̠ku̠ku̠, igurumia̠n ologi, igelemeni, ipesi, a̠gbokia̠n, o̠gba o̠ni̠ o̠pi̠e̠, i̠re̠ma (obhuneni, o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ozu), ema̠ (esusula̠). \wj* 
\v 23 \wj Eb̠la̠ i̠karabh i̠nye̠n na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi na̠ emite sa̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ima̠ra̠ Ologi Ani̠ ola̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠zu 
\r (Amatiu 15:21-28) 
\p  
\v 24 A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Ataya sa̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠loghom, ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠wo̠gi̠na.  
\v 25 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, ani̠ ola̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh a̠nyegi ma̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ amu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠mel agu̠ran d̠a̠ a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 26 Ani̠ bho̠ ola̠ A̠zu d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ ola̠ A̠fonisia̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠siria̠, sa̠ ale̠gh A̠zizo̠s ma̠ oze o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ozu o̠nyani̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ ed̠ia̠ ed̠e elegha̠n, na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ obhin ed̠ia̠n anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ orobhod̠i onigha̠ a̠sib̠ogho.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, a̠sib̠ogho ya̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ekpukpu akpata od̠e bho̠ eka̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ na̠ emeleghu bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “D̠a̠ ebula̠ awo̠ran d̠oyom, gi̠e̠, o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ ozu o̠nyani̠ d̠oyom.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ abi̠gh ka̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ na̠ amanaghan d̠a̠ e̠mana, sa̠ abi̠gh nyen ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ ozu o̠nyani̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ o̠b̠aghab̠agh emua̠ o̠ni̠ 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mula̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ eghighira̠ Ataya agi̠ d̠a̠ agba A̠sido̠n d̠a̠ abadi̠ Agalili wa̠ a̠tua̠n Ebhugh A̠d̠iobh Re̠ma bho̠.  
\v 32 Sa̠ idi a̠nwunom ibhin o̠b̠aghab̠agh o̠ni̠ ola̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mar ofugh a̠fugh iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na, i̠le̠gh agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ agbam agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin i̠na d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ aka, sa̠ azo̠l asu̠nu̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ra̠to o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ asi̠r i̠gho̠r d̠a̠ ad̠u̠nu̠ agu̠o̠ a̠bhin a̠kula̠n a̠nem o̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny afi̠o̠ghu̠, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “E̠fata!” \wj*\f + \fr 7:34 \fq E̠fata: \ft Ekpo a̠fugh onon bha̠ o̠nu̠ Aramai̠k, o̠nu̠ e̠ma ola̠ a̠nwunom Apale̠stai̠n d̠a̠ amu̠m ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.\f* (a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Guruna̠!” \wj*)  
\v 35 Sa̠ ra̠to o̠ni̠ bho̠ iguruna̠ epa̠, sa̠ abar wa̠ na̠ a̠sibhom a̠nem d̠o̠yo̠ ako̠ti̠na, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh abar geregere. 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s aghaghana ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠, awa o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ imite bho̠ e̠sasaragi̠, ya̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠bhin aghaghana awa bho̠, bha̠ agu̠o̠ awa ibhin i̠gba i̠sasaragi̠.  
\v 37 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n a̠nwunom. Sa̠ awa i̠gba ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ amar a̠gir eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar. Remua̠ bho̠ na̠ efugh a̠fugh, sa̠ i̠b̠aghab̠agh bho̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n abar.” 
\c 8  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠nigha̠ ma̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠r a̠nwunom ed̠ia̠n 
\r (Amatiu 15:32-39) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom emula̠ ekokod̠ia̠n na̠ i̠na, ma̠ ola̠ abar ola̠ awa ta̠ ed̠e na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 2 \wj “Igbirigbir a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ed̠ighi ami̠, ezin bho̠ awa na̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ ami̠ i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ unwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ awa ta̠ ed̠e.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠ ami̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠ oyel o̠ko̠i̠, bha̠ idi ta̠ e̠fu̠mu̠ d̠a̠ eten bho̠. Idi awa i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ esi egbeiny eru.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar ta̠ orue o̠te̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠ken, d̠a̠ esi ola̠ kukunum o̠ko̠no̠n, ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ elei awa ma̠ od̠e?” 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin unwuna̠ ma̠ i̠ni̠ ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Od̠ua̠l.” 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ a̠de, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin od̠ua̠l ikpogh abre̠di̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ali̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠pupugion a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ma̠ o̠ru̠gi̠, sa̠ awa i̠ru̠gi̠ inigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 7 O̠nyi̠ki̠kara i̠gbara ina̠ e̠ro̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠tutumeni a̠ruom awa nyen o̠ru̠gi̠.  
\v 8 Sa̠ awa id̠e, sa̠ id̠e ilegha̠n. Ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ikpokpo ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r isughia̠n bho̠, bha̠ ilei od̠ua̠l a̠rukpuom.  
\v 9 A̠nwunom bho̠ ilei agu̠o̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠r (4,000) o̠ni̠\f + \fr 8:9 \fl Obhin o̠tu̠ghan \ft od̠i nyen. Amat 15:32-39. D̠iobh o̠ni̠r (4,000) bho̠ bha̠ ilobhiri ku̠ku̠m, Amaki̠ na̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠mutiom.\f*, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom awa ma̠ oten oyel.  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Adalmanuta\f + \fr 8:10 \fl Obhin o̠tu̠ghan \ft Ta̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ologhom a̠ga̠i esi wa̠ \ft \+it Adalmanuta\+it* od̠i bho̠, iya̠ od̠i ma̠ esi ola̠ a̠tua̠n Abadi̠ Agalili.\f*. 
\s1 Rafarisi bho̠ ipuru ma̠ Elegh 
\r (Amatiu 16:1-4) 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ iru sa̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠anan o̠yo̠. D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠d̠a o̠yo̠ okpon, sa̠ awa ipuru ma̠ i̠na a̠leriom elegh ola̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru.  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na afi̠o̠ghu̠ ma̠ ibom d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj “Ezin ka̠ ere ma̠ ola̠ amu̠m onon na̠ epuru ma̠ elegh bho̠? Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ elegh ola̠ ta̠ onigha̠ ma̠ amu̠m onon bo̠.”\wj* 
\v 13 Sa̠ i̠na awe̠le̠man awa ad̠u̠a ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh ab̠e̠i̠ d̠a̠ agba uwed̠i. 
\s1 A̠yist Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ E̠ro̠d 
\r (Amatiu 16:5-12) 
\p  
\v 14 Awa iweleta̠n obhin ed̠ia̠n, a̠sigimeni ma̠ onin ekpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ ola̠ awa inwuna̠ d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠.  
\v 15 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kikiom awa agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Ilelegi, ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ a̠yist ta̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ a̠yist ta̠ E̠ro̠d.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ awa id̠igh i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an ma̠a̠, “Agu̠o̠ i̠yar onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.”  
\v 17 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠nyan, sa̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ezin ka̠ ere ma̠ ola̠ inyin na̠ o̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an ogboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠? I̠se̠n eka̠ bha̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan ke̠re̠? Rologi d̠inyin ta̠ okperina̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? \wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ikpo a̠rid̠ien od̠i inyin, ya̠a̠ inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh abar ke̠re̠? Ra̠to od̠i inyin, ya̠a̠ inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n abar ke̠re̠? Inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an ke̠re̠? \wj* 
\v 19 \wj Obhel bho̠ ami̠ ipuinyogh ogho ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ inigha̠ ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala (5,000) o̠nu̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, ka̠ i̠ni̠ a̠rukpuom i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r isughia̠n ya̠ inyin ukpokpo?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠, “D̠iobh na̠ i̠wal.” 
\p  
\v 20 \wj “Obhel bho̠ ami̠ ibhin od̠ua̠l ikoko ma̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠r bho̠, ka̠ inyin ukpokpo ma̠ i̠ni̠ a̠rukpuom i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r isughia̠n?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Od̠ua̠l.” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ nyen, ke̠re̠?”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ O̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien d̠a̠ Abe̠tsai̠da 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ awa iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠tsai̠da. Sa̠ idi a̠nwunom ibhin o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien iru ra̠ i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠ okula̠n o̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na a̠sibh o̠ni̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠rileghom ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠, asi̠r i̠gho̠r d̠a̠ a̠rid̠ien o̠ni̠ bho̠, a̠bhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠puom a̠rid̠ien o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa na̠ abi̠gh abar ke̠re̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon d̠a̠ anyu̠, sa̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ abi̠gh a̠nwunom agu̠o̠ iriren iya̠ na̠ erile.” 
\p  
\v 25 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠puta̠ a̠bhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠puom a̠rid̠ien o̠ni̠ bho̠. Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠kimigi a̠kpon, sa̠ a̠rid̠ien bho̠ imula̠ ibhon, sa̠ amar abi̠gh eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar geregere.  
\v 26 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom i̠na ma̠a̠, i̠na a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ aghaghana i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Ko od̠igh mu d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠.” \wj* 
\s1 A̠puta̠ agba ma̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mutiom 
\r (Amatiu 16:18-21) 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠d̠u̠a i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma A̠sizeria̠ A̠filipai̠ bho̠. Agu̠o̠ awa na̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠nwunom na̠ e̠gba ma̠ ami̠ ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠; ipa̠n ma̠a̠, I̠lai̠za; ya̠a̠ idi na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, odi owil bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ami̠ ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ A̠puta̠ agba a̠mutiom ma̠a̠, “Anwa Akrai̠st.” 
\p  
\v 30 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s aghaghana awa ma̠a̠, awa obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ igboloma̠ i̠na e̠gba enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Omugh d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 16:21-28; A̠luk 9:22-27) 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ akpe̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbika̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar, sa̠ ikei bho̠ na̠ aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ ta̠ eghel i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ egigh i̠na, sa̠ ka̠ i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ eten, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠.  
\v 32 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ agba ma̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ asi̠si̠ghe̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ A̠puta̠ a̠bhin i̠na ma̠ o̠nu̠ ma̠a̠, i̠na ofugh d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a. 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ awo̠ran A̠puta̠ ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Eru bho̠, tene d̠a̠ aman d̠ami̠! Ezin bho̠ anwa na̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠o̠m abar, ya̠a̠ iya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Eten E̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an Oriren bho̠ 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kokod̠i ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ ebhir o̠tu̠o̠no̠m ami̠ ta̠ aku̠a ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ aman, sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠eton e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren d̠o̠yo̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ ato̠ma ma̠ okighom a̠ghud̠um e̠mara̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ta̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ orobh a̠ghud̠um e̠mara̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ ami̠ na̠ ebula̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠, ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul. \wj* 
\v 36 \wj Asu̠o̠ bho̠ ka̠ ere, ka̠ o̠ni̠ ate̠i̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon, sa̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠? \wj* 
\v 37 \wj Ere ta̠ a̠lei o̠ni̠ ma̠ obhin onwegia̠n a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠? \wj* 
\v 38 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠din ami̠ na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠ami̠ a̠d̠igh ari̠ghe̠l d̠a̠ amu̠m onon wa̠ od̠umom d̠a̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, na̠ erugh i̠karabh ado̠l bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ eka̠ ta̠ a̠din i̠na a̠d̠igh ari̠ghe̠l ma̠ obhel itileduom e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ta̠ ed̠igh na̠ i̠na eru d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠.”\wj* 
\c 9  
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ idi inyin ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠ ko omugh d̠o̠ tu̠tu̠n awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh ka̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ná̠ a̠ru na̠ a̠limon.” \wj* 
\s1 Ozu isosorogia̠n ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 17:1-13; A̠luk 9:28-36) 
\p  
\v 2 Odin a̠d̠a̠ma̠ iten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin A̠pita̠, na̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n asi̠n igu ola̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠, d̠a̠ esi ola̠ awa ku̠ku̠m i̠ro̠. I̠se̠ sa̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nwegia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠awa.  
\v 3 Sa̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ i̠b̠al, i̠mu̠, isosorogia̠n ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ bebina̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠de onon ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a bo̠.  
\v 4 Sa̠ I̠lai̠za na̠ A̠mozizi imite ma̠ i̠se̠ ra̠ id̠igh na̠ A̠zizo̠s i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an. 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, agu̠o̠ a̠bhon i̠yar o̠ro̠ i̠se̠n! D̠ighi i̠yar ogim i̠sar a̠rutu akpu̠ru̠: odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ oyom, odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠mozizi, sa̠ odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ I̠lai̠za.”  
\v 6 (Ezin bho̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa ka̠ e̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ A̠pita̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ ofugh). 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh a̠kpegiom awa. Sa̠ okoroko a̠si d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Onon O̠nyi̠ etula̠n d̠ami̠. I̠nagha i̠na!” 
\p  
\v 8 D̠a̠ awai̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh ka̠ A̠zizo̠s ku̠ku̠m od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠. 
\p  
\v 9 Agu̠o̠ awa na̠ esor d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s aghaghana awa ma̠a̠, awa o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ awa i̠bi̠gh bho̠ enigha̠ bebina̠ o̠ni̠, a̠ten ka̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.  
\v 10 Sa̠ awa ikighom abar bho̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa, sa̠ awa iguri i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an igboloma̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ “Ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh” a̠ma̠ra̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ere wa̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ I̠lai̠za ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠ru bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, I̠lai̠za ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠ru, ra̠ a̠selegi ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar. Ere wa̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠a̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠gbika̠ ma̠ ibom sa̠ ta̠ oghel bho̠?\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠; I̠lai̠za a̠ru, sa̠ awa ikpon abar abar igir igboloma̠ i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠ ta̠ emutuma̠ i̠na bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ozu od̠i o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ 
\r (Amatiu 17:14-20; A̠luk 9:37-43) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ awa iru d̠a̠ ogbo atu̠ghan iyed̠i, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ eko awa ikiton, ya̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ e̠ku̠anan awa.  
\v 15 I̠se̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠na sa̠ id̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n ma̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠yo̠, sa̠ ikpo ma̠ eghil ka̠ ibheleguma̠ i̠na. 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n o̠lo̠gh bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠ku̠anan awa ma̠ ere?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ ibhin o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ ola̠ e̠mu̠gh emua̠ na̠ anyo̠gho̠gh a̠ru d̠oyom.  
\v 18 Ka̠ e̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠puom i̠na, sa̠ na̠ agu̠ro̠m i̠na, sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠fuko d̠a̠ o̠nu̠, na̠ aghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ ozu bho̠ na̠ a̠kpari̠an. Sa̠ ami̠ iruom ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom ma̠ oze o̠si̠ghe̠, ya̠a̠ irue d̠o̠.” 
\p  
\v 19 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Sei! Amu̠m ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠to̠! Ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ na̠ inyin a̠bia̠ eka̠, kisa̠ inyin ta̠ oma̠ra̠? Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ne ma̠ ado̠l ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠to̠ d̠inyin a̠bia̠ eka̠? Ibhine ma̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠ eru.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ awa ibhin i̠na i̠gi̠. Agu̠o̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ abi̠gh A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ agu̠ro̠m epa̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠de sa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ asasalaghu̠, a̠kikila̠, a̠fuko ma̠ i̠gho̠r. 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n o̠we̠de̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Abar onon ka̠ ake̠ ma̠ a̠kere obhel od̠ighi o̠yo̠?”\wj* Sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ake̠ d̠a̠ i̠gbara d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 22 Na̠ a̠robh gha̠n i̠na na̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ anya na̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogigh o̠yo̠. O̠ku̠a eka̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ anwa ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir abar a̠gboloma̠, bha̠ kpone i̠yar igbirigbir ma̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar.” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa i̠tu̠n ere na̠ a̠pura̠n ka̠ ‘anwa ta̠ a̠rue’? Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ anwa a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠, kabar kabar ta̠ a̠rue a̠mite.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ a̠d̠umom; ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠ami̠ olei d̠a̠ eka̠, bhe̠le̠ ami̠!” 
\p  
\v 25 A̠zizo̠s ra̠ abi̠gh ma̠a̠, o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom na̠ eghil na̠ eru bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa e̠mu̠gh emua̠ na̠ ab̠agh, ami̠ na̠ a̠mulughuom anwa, d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠nyi̠ bho̠, ka̠ onyegi mu i̠na.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ e̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠mulughu, sa̠ alo̠gh e̠mi̠ a̠nuoghom i̠na ma̠ o̠si̠si̠laghu̠, sa̠ a̠mite ad̠u̠a. Sa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ aro̠ woma̠ na̠ a̠mugh, ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ i̠na na̠ a̠mugh.  
\v 27 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠sibh i̠na d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠b̠eton, sa̠ amara. 
\p  
\v 28 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ipura̠n i̠na d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ma̠a̠, “Ere wa̠ i̠yar orue d̠o̠ ma̠ oze o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ola̠ o̠ko̠no̠n ka̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠, a̠ten a̠siseiny.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠mula̠ a̠wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Omugh d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 17:22,23; A̠luk 9:43-45) 
\p  
\v 30 A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ agi̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ i̠na o̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠loghom. I̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ Agalili,  
\v 31 ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ abar. Sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ogbo i̠to̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ egigh, sa̠ ta̠ egigh i̠na. Sa̠ d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠.”\wj* 
\v 32 Awa i̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ iwowa̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ ighil opura̠n o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 33 Awa ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ Akapani̠o̠m, sa̠ id̠igh d̠a̠ otu. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin u̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an ere d̠a̠ eten bho̠?”\wj* 
\v 34 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠ro̠ b̠u̠b̠o̠m, ezin bho̠ awa i̠ku̠anan igboloma̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa bho̠.  
\v 35 Sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, sa̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠ro̠ o̠pu̠r, bha̠ i̠na a̠d̠ia̠ aro̠ ma̠ wa̠ o̠gu̠man na̠ agu̠o̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ amarame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, sa̠ a̠sibh agu̠o̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠ni̠gha̠ awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 37 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ atu̠n a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ ada ma̠ odi d̠a̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny i̠nye̠n a̠bhin, bha̠ ada ami̠ a̠bhin. O̠ni̠ ola̠ ada ami̠ a̠bhin, bha̠ na̠ o̠da d̠o̠ ka̠ ami̠ a̠bhin, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ruom ami̠ bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 O̠ni̠ ola̠ owia̠n d̠o̠ i̠yar bha̠ od̠i na̠ i̠yar 
\r (A̠luk 9:49,50) 
\p  
\v 38 Azo̠n agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠yar u̠bi̠gh ka̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien d̠oyom na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru, sa̠ i̠yar ukigima̠ i̠na, ezin bho̠ i̠na bo̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠i̠yar.”  
\v 39 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ko okigima̠ i̠na, ezin bho̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ a̠gir ilologia̠n ko o̠nu̠r d̠o̠ epa̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ami̠.\wj* 
\v 40 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ owia̠n d̠o̠ i̠yar bha̠ od̠i na̠ i̠yar.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ atu̠n a̠d̠ien ta̠ Akrai̠st a̠nigha̠ inyin okpa̠ko amu̠m ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ad̠agi̠an ya̠ ogir i̠karabh 
\p  
\v 42 \wj O̠gho̠ro̠gi̠o̠m o̠gbe̠o̠ma d̠a̠ orum o̠ni̠ orobh o̠ni̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ abadi̠, ta̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ ta̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ odi o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ ola̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ami̠, ma̠ omel od̠igh d̠a̠ i̠karabh.\wj* 
\v 43-44 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam omel o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sobhe ma̠ asi̠ghe̠. Anwa ma̠ obhin e̠gha ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ obhin i̠wal aru̠gu̠o̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ e̠banya, wa̠ ka̠ od̠im d̠o̠ bho̠.\wj*\f + \fr 9:43-44 \ft Idi i̠pu̠r ra̠d̠ire bho̠ i̠lo̠gho̠m ma̠ 44: esi wa̠, “Igbukuma̠ ya̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠ ko omugh d̠o̠, sa̠ anya bho̠ od̠im d̠o̠ bho̠.” Kpone d̠a̠ 48\f* 
\v 45-46 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠ a̠wel d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam omel o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sobhe ma̠ asi̠ghe̠. Anwa ma̠ o̠ro̠ ukula̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ onwuna̠ i̠wal a̠sike, sa̠ ta̠ orobh anwa o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠banya.\wj*\f + \fr 9:45-46 \ft Idi ra̠d̠ire bho̠ i̠lo̠gho̠m ma̠ 46: esi wa̠ “Igbukuma̠ ya̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠ ko omugh d̠o̠, sa̠ anya bho̠ od̠im d̠o̠ bho̠.” Kpone d̠a̠ o̠gbu̠r 48. \f* 
\v 47 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam omel o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠, poko ma̠ asi̠ghe̠. Anwa ma̠ obhin onin ekpo a̠d̠ien od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ owuna̠ i̠wal a̠rid̠ien, sa̠ ta̠ orobh anwa o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠banya, \wj* 
\v 48 \wj “Esi wa̠ igbukuma̠ ya̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠ ko omugh d̠o̠, sa̠ anya bho̠ od̠im d̠o̠ bho̠.” \wj*\f + \fr 9:48 \ft \xt Azaya 66:24\f*\x - \xo 9:48 \xt Azaya 66:24\x* 
\p  
\v 49 \wj Ta̠ obhin anya o̠sa ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ o̠me̠me̠ni̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ obhin ub̠on na̠ o̠me̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠. \wj* 
\v 50 \wj “Ub̠on ob̠eb̠i abar, ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ub̠on bho̠ na̠ a̠robh a̠lisibh d̠o̠yo̠, ka̠ ub̠on bho̠ ta̠ ed̠ighi eka̠ emula̠ esibh? Inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lisibh ta̠ ub̠on d̠a̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin, ya̠ ekima̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin.”\wj* 
\c 10  
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ iya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Ogbogina̠ Ilom 
\r (Amatiu 19:1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠zudia̠, sa̠ ab̠e̠i̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ Azo̠dan. Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ipita̠ iko i̠na ikiton, sa̠ a̠puta̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir gha̠n bho̠. 
\p  
\v 2 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ iru ma̠ o̠da o̠yo̠ okpon, sa̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Owolom ta̠ a̠rue a̠soroni ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠mozizi agba eka̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ogbogina̠ ilom?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “A̠mozizi a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ onigha̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ire ogbogina̠ ilom, obhin osoroni ani̠.” 
\p  
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠mozizi a̠din ab̠agh e̠mu̠ d̠inyin age̠ ma̠ oloko obha̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin. \wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ale̠m awa ma̠ ‘o̠ya na̠ olobhiri.’\wj*\f + \fr 10:6 \ft \xt Ob̠et 1:27\f* 
\v 7 \wj ‘Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, olobhiri o̠ni̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠ ma̠ oweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ ab̠araguma ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠,\wj* 
\v 8 \wj sa̠ i̠wal awa ta̠ eten onin ozu.’ O̠ku̠a bha̠ awa bo̠mu̠ i̠wal, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ awa na̠ eten onin ozu.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, abar wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ atu̠lo̠m bho̠, o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ o̠bagi̠o̠n d̠o̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 10 Igiel bha̠ awa imula̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na igboloma̠ ma̠ abar onon.  
\v 11 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠soroni ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ a̠bhin opa̠n, bha̠ a̠sor oloko od̠e e̠ma a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ani̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ani̠ ola̠ a̠gbogina̠ ma̠ owolom d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ awal opa̠n, a̠sor oloko od̠e e̠ma.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠tutumeni ma̠ I̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny 
\r (Amatiu 19:13-15; A̠luk 18:15-17) 
\p  
\v 13 A̠nwunom ibhin i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny d̠awa eru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠kula̠n awa, ya̠a̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠b̠ab̠agi̠na ikigima̠ awa. 
\p  
\v 14 A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ agam a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ima̠ra̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ eru d̠ami̠, ya̠a̠ ka̠ okigima̠ awa, ezin bho̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠da d̠o̠ ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin agu̠o̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ologi.”\wj* 
\v 16 Sa̠ a̠b̠ola̠n o̠gbara o̠nyi̠, o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ i̠se̠, agbam agu̠o̠ a̠tutumeni. 
\s1 O̠li̠la O̠ni̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 19:16-30; A̠luk 18:18-30) 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ erile, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠kpo ma̠ eghil ka̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n i̠na a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ere ma̠ abar wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠?” 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa na̠ atu̠n ere na̠ a̠bhelegi ami̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠? O̠ni̠ ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i bo̠, a̠ten A̠zib̠a̠.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Anwa a̠loghom roloko bho̠: ‘Ko ogigh o̠ni̠, ko od̠e ma̠ e̠ma, ko ob̠igh a̠b̠igh, ko o̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ igunugha̠, ko oniniom o̠ni̠, zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom.’\wj*\f + \fr 10:19 \ft \xt E̠d̠u̠a 20:12-16\ft ; \xt Oloko 5:16-20\f*\wj ”\wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠koko ma̠ roloko i̠nye̠n keka̠ d̠a̠ i̠gbara d̠ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin obhel a̠kpon i̠na, sa̠ a̠ba̠ra̠ i̠na, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Onin abar a̠sugho, gi̠e̠ ka̠ a̠wol eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa inwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠, sa̠ anwa ta̠ ate̠i̠ e̠li̠la d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, ma̠ a̠ru ra̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠zum d̠a̠ ebula̠ awo̠ran bho̠, sa̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a, ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠gbo ma̠ ibom e̠li̠la. 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kpon ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gir sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Agu̠o̠ akpar aru̠lala ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠. Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mula̠ alo̠gho̠m ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwi̠i̠ny d̠ami̠, amar akpar od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠!\wj* 
\v 25 \wj A̠b̠ur e̠nam a̠dol o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ oyol anu̠ga oten a̠pu ma̠ o̠li̠la ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ awa imula̠ ib̠ogina̠ ma̠ o̠gbam, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠pura̠n odi ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ a̠nyen ta̠ a̠rue a̠ten?” 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin obhel a̠kpon awa awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “D̠a̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ bha̠ na̠ orue d̠o̠ a̠mite, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠o̠, d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ kabar kabar ta̠ a̠rue a̠mite.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠puta̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Kpone! I̠yar na̠ o̠we̠le̠man kabar kabar na̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m anwa!” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ awe̠le̠man eghun otu, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠rumor, bo̠d̠o̠ aru̠marani̠, bo̠d̠o̠ onweni, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠, bo̠d̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny, bo̠d̠o̠ od̠ighi, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ami̠ na̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠, \wj* 
\v 30 \wj ola̠ ko o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh igiel ma̠ i̠se̠n d̠a̠ obhel onon bo̠: a̠d̠igh eghun otu, a̠rumor, aru̠marani̠, onweni, anwi̠i̠ny, a̠de od̠ighi na̠ a̠nwunom oponoma̠ ogbikimeni o̠yo̠ nyen, na̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul d̠a̠ amu̠m wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Ya̠a̠, a̠d̠izo ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ta̠ eten d̠a̠ aman, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ aman bho̠ ta̠ eten d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Oleghemeni i̠sar igiel  //  A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 20:17-19; A̠luk 18:31-34) 
\p  
\v 32 D̠a̠ obhel bho̠ awa na̠ eten na̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠, A̠zizo̠s aro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠a̠ awa. Sa̠ ekpoyogh ologi na̠ a̠rugugu isibh ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠puta̠ a̠bhin d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ aka, sa̠ ake̠ ma̠ o̠gba i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ eru ra̠ omutuma̠ o̠yo̠ bho̠ onigha̠ awa,  
\v 33 ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠nagha o! I̠yar na̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, sa̠ ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ esobh ase̠ omugh ebhumeni i̠na. Ta̠ eb̠eton i̠na o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ibhebhia̠n bho̠, \wj* 
\v 34 \wj sa̠ ta̠ e̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ emurughom i̠na ma̠ i̠gho̠r, sa̠ ta̠ e̠gu̠ro̠gh i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ egigh i̠na, a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠ sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh!”\wj* 
\s1 Ipuru ta̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n 
\r (Amatiu 20:20-28) 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n, anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ Aze̠bidi iru d̠a̠ o̠yo̠ ra̠ ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ i̠yar kabar kabar ola̠ i̠yar upuru nyam.” 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Ere ma̠ abar wa̠ inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh ami̠ ma̠ ogir onigha̠ inyin bho̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “D̠ighi odi i̠yar aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom d̠oyom, sa̠ uwed̠i ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ okiel d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n d̠oyom.” 
\p  
\v 38 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin u̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ inyin na̠ opuru bho̠. Inyin ta̠ orue o̠d̠a d̠a̠ okpa̠ko wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ ad̠a bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠d̠ien owura̠ amu̠m wa̠ ta̠ owur ami̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠yar ta̠ orue.” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ta̠ o̠d̠a d̠a̠ okpa̠ko wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ ad̠a bho̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ owura̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien amu̠m wa̠ ta̠ owur ami̠ bho̠,\wj* 
\v 40 \wj ya̠a̠, o̠ro̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom d̠ami̠ bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ okiel d̠ami̠, bha̠ ami̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ ato̠ bho̠ d̠o̠. A̠dila̠de i̠nye̠n i̠ro̠ inigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ oguri osisa̠n bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 41 Igiel wa̠ d̠iobh ogbo ogir iyed̠i i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ rologi d̠awa igurom inigha̠ ma̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n. 
\p  
\v 42 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi awa agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ologhom ma̠a̠, ogbo aru̠mu̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon i̠to̠ egboloma̠ awa, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠bu̠gh e̠mi̠ bho̠ na̠ eponoma̠ awa.\wj* 
\v 43 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠bu̠gh e̠mi̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin bho̠, aro̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠inyin,\wj* 
\v 44 \wj sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠ro̠ o̠pu̠r, a̠d̠ia̠ aro̠ ma̠ e̠bana ta̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwu̠nom.\wj* 
\v 45 \wj Ezin bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ oru d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠ro̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠ru ma̠ o̠ro̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu onigha̠ a̠nwunom, na̠ onigha̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ obhin o̠ta a̠d̠izo ogbo.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠likoko ikpom a̠rid̠ien ta̠ Abatimi̠o̠s 
\r (Amatiu 20:29-34; A̠luk 18:35-43) 
\p  
\v 46 Sa̠ awa iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Aze̠riko. Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ Aze̠riko bho̠, bha̠ Abatimi̠o̠s o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠timi̠o̠s aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ aka eten, na̠ a̠puru ma̠ ipupuru.  
\v 47 Igiel bho̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n ma̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anazare̠t na̠ a̠ten bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ izul, a̠mulughu ma̠a̠, “A̠zizo̠s, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 48 Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠b̠ab̠agi̠na i̠na ma̠a̠ i̠na a̠nima̠, ya̠a̠, i̠na alo̠gh e̠mi̠ omulughu ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 49 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s amara kpom, sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠ obhelegi o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien bho̠ oruom o̠yo̠, sa̠ awa ibhelegi i̠na i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Kpo̠luzu! B̠etina̠! I̠na na̠ a̠bhelegi nyam.”  
\v 50 Sa̠ i̠na ake̠gi̠na ma̠ akapa anyu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠robh, sa̠ a̠pel amara a̠rile agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s. 
\p  
\v 51 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠gh ami̠ ma̠ ogir ere onigha̠ oyom?”\wj* Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “We̠mu̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh omula̠ o̠bi̠gh abar.” 
\p  
\v 52 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Yele, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠koko nyam.”\wj* Ogbo na̠ onin, sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ abi̠gh abar, sa̠ i̠na atu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ eten bho̠. 
\c 11  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m agu̠o̠ O̠li̠le̠ma 
\r (Amatiu 21:1-11; A̠luk 19:28-40; Azo̠n 12:12-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ eten na̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, sa̠ iru ra̠ itua̠n Abe̠ti̠fagi̠ na̠ Abe̠tani d̠a̠ aka Igu Oliv bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ od̠ia̠ o̠gi̠ na̠ awa,  
\v 2 sa̠ agba a̠nigha awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma wa̠ a̠sumogha̠n inyin bho̠. Sa̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ od̠igh bho̠, inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠nyi̠ ado̠ki̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ a̠rile. I̠ko̠to̠ne̠ ma̠ ado̠ki̠ bho̠ ma̠ ebhin eru.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Sa̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ a̠pura̠n inyin ma̠a̠, ‘Inyin na̠ udin ere na̠ ogir abar onon?’ Ma̠ e̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh orughom, sa̠ ta̠ anu̠r a̠mulumeni a̠ru ma̠ i̠se̠n i̠se̠n.’ ” \wj* 
\v 4 Sa̠ awa iten i̠gi̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh o̠nyi̠ ado̠ki̠ ola̠ na̠ o̠kpo̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ogigo d̠a̠ aka eten bho̠. Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠ko̠to̠n bho̠,  
\v 5 sa̠ idi a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠ ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ odin ere na̠ o̠ko̠to̠n o̠nyi̠ ado̠ki̠ bho̠?”  
\v 6 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom awa bho̠, sa̠ ima̠ra̠ awa ma̠ obhin.  
\v 7 Sa̠ awa ibhin o̠nyi̠ ado̠ki̠ bho̠ iruom A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ i̠gbamagi̠ ma̠ rakapa anyu̠ d̠awa d̠a̠ anyu̠ e̠nam bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s asi̠n d̠a̠ anyu̠ e̠nam bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de.  
\v 8 A̠d̠izo a̠nwunom i̠de̠ ma̠ rakapa anyu̠ d̠awa d̠a̠ eten bho̠, sa̠ ipa̠n ogbo igbodo ma̠ ra̠to iriren d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠ ibhin i̠de̠ d̠a̠ eten bho̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ bho̠ na̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ aman bho̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ omulughu o̠gba okue ma̠a̠, “Ozana!\f + \fr 11:9 \ft Ezin ta̠ Ozana bha̠ tenemeni i̠yar i̠se̠n bo̠d̠o̠ itutumeni. \f* Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠! A̠zib̠a̠ a̠tutumeni i̠na wa̠ na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠!  
\v 10 E̠no̠gho̠man e̠te̠i̠ irileghom ta̠ obom o̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar A̠devidi wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠. Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ a̠pu bho̠!”  
\v 11 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ogigo Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠kpon a̠kitineni abi̠gh agu̠o̠ i̠di̠ar od̠i. Ya̠a̠ agu̠o̠ obhel bho̠ na̠ a̠ten a̠pu d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠rogi ma̠ oriren a̠fig 
\r (Amatiu 21:1-9) 
\p  
\v 12 I̠b̠ala bho̠, ma̠ igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ Abe̠tani na̠ emula̠ na̠ eru bho̠, sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na.  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ egbeiny abi̠gh oriren a̠fig ola̠ ra̠to a̠to imuzo, sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠ighoma̠ ka̠ i̠na ta̠ abi̠gh itu. Igiel bho̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ bho̠, i̠na na̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ bebina̠ otu oriren a̠ten ra̠to, ezin bho̠ ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel ra̠fig.  
\v 14 Sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠fig bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ o̠bi̠gh mu̠ ma̠ otu d̠oyom a̠d̠e tu̠tu̠n kid̠ud̠ul!” \wj* Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n i̠na. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\r (Amatiu 21:12-17; A̠luk 19:5-48; Azo̠n 2:13-22) 
\p  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ awa imisi d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ ozegi eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eghoyogh i̠di̠ar na̠ eb̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠b̠ua̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠. I̠na a̠kpululeni ma̠ rakpata a̠b̠ua̠ ta̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ enwegi ma̠ ikpoki bho̠ na̠ ri̠kasi̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ewod̠i ma̠ rukurosege bho̠.  
\v 16 Sa̠ na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin abar a̠b̠ua̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ rogigo Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠na atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, \wj “U̠ge̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Ta̠ obhelegi ma̠ otu d̠ami̠ ma̠ otu a̠siseiny eb̠la̠ ra̠dede’? Ya̠a̠, inyin na̠ otenemeni ma̠ e̠fe̠m ib̠igh ma̠ a̠b̠igh!” \wj*\f + \fr 11:17 \ft \xt Azaya 56:7\f* 
\v 18 Igiel bho̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan agu̠o̠ obhin ogigh A̠zizo̠s. Awa ighil i̠na, ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ema̠gha̠ ma̠ ebula̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 19 Ate̠i̠ a̠dule, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠. 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oriren a̠fig bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 21:20-22) 
\p  
\v 20 I̠b̠ala bho̠ ma̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠, ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa na̠ erile d̠a̠ eten bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh oriren a̠fig bho̠ ka̠ na̠ aghi̠ghara d̠a̠ eb̠o a̠sor d̠a̠ i̠ki̠ka bho̠.  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠puta̠ aru̠ru̠an abar wa̠ a̠mite bho̠ sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, kpone! Oriren a̠fig wa̠ anwa irogi bho̠ na̠ aghi̠ghara.”  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Inwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” \wj* 
\v 23 \wj “Ya̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ igu onon ma̠, ‘B̠uruna̠ ka̠ a̠mel d̠a̠ abadi̠,’ sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ i̠wal rologi, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠ma̠ra̠, bha̠ omite epa̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a. \wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, kabar kabar ola̠ inyin na̠ esiseiny na̠ opuru, bha̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ inyin na̠ o̠te̠i̠ abar bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mite ma̠ o̠ku̠a a̠nigha̠ inyin. \wj* 
\v 25 \wj Igiel inyin ub̠etina̠ u̠mara ma̠ osiseiny a̠siseiny, bha̠ i̠we̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ i̠karabh ya̠ inyin unwuna̠ ugboloma̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, b̠o̠ka̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ eka̠ awe̠le̠man i̠karabh od̠ighi̠ i̠di̠ar d̠oyom. \wj* [ 
\v 26 \wj Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ anwa na̠ o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh opa̠n o̠ni̠, bha̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ eka̠ ko o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh od̠ighi̠ i̠di̠ar d̠oyom.”\wj*] 
\s1 Ipura̠n a̠dila̠de a̠limon ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 21:23-27; A̠luk 20:1-8) 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠ imula̠ iru d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m. Agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rile na̠ a̠gir d̠a̠ ologi Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, na̠ ikei bho̠, iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na,  
\v 28 sa̠ ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ a̠bhin a̠kere a̠d̠ien a̠limon na̠ a̠gir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n? A̠nyen a̠nigha̠ nyam a̠limon obhin ogir ogir i̠nye̠n?” 
\p  
\v 29 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ onin ipura̠n ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠pura̠n inyin. Ka̠ inyin u̠wo̠ran, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ agba ma̠ esi bho̠ ami̠ i̠te̠i̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ na̠ a̠gir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Owura̠ amu̠m ta̠ Azo̠n ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠? I̠wo̠rane̠ Ami̠!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ awa ibhin i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ i̠yar u̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠pura̠n i̠yar ma̠a̠, ‘Inyin udin ere o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ oma̠ra̠ asu̠gbagba ta̠ Azo̠n?’  
\v 32 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ i̠yar u̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ a̠ru’ ...” (Awa ighil a̠nwunom bho̠, ezin bho̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ Azo̠n owil ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.)  
\v 33 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “I̠yar uloghom d̠o̠.” Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ eka̠ ami̠ ko o̠gba d̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin a̠dila̠de a̠limon wa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin na̠ a̠gir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠.” \wj* 
\c 12  
\s1 A̠sidogh ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei a̠grep bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 21:33-46; A̠luk 20:9-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ orogh a̠sidogh onigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “Odi o̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠gbebh ra̠grep d̠a̠ a̠lei d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ a̠ko ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ a̠kiton, sa̠ a̠gbo ma̠ ogugua̠ ola̠ omumogh a̠min a̠grep bho̠ omutiom. I̠na a̠lo ma̠ otu ipoiny nyen, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠ko̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ agi̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n ebhugh. \wj* 
\v 2 \wj Igiel bho̠ a̠lei obhel o̠ku̠ a̠grep bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠limon odi e̠bana d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ obhin a̠bin imuma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ oru. \wj* 
\v 3 \wj Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ipuom i̠na, sa̠ id̠ul, sa̠ imulumeni i̠na ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠. \wj* 
\v 4 \wj Opa̠n igiel, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠limon opa̠n e̠bana d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ obhin a̠bin imuma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ oru. Sa̠ awa id̠ul i̠na, ib̠om e̠mu̠, i̠lo̠gh i̠na ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l. \wj* 
\v 5 \wj Sa̠ a̠puta̠ a̠ruom opa̠n e̠bana ma̠ o̠gi̠, sa̠ awa igigh obha̠. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ awa id̠ulogh ipa̠n iya̠ uruom, ya̠a̠ i̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ idi. \wj* 
\p  
\v 6 \wj “Opa̠n o̠ni̠ ola̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ oruom bo̠, a̠ten ogini o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ wa̠ i̠na a̠tula̠n ibom bho̠. Ekunuguma̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠limon o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ awa, ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ awa ta̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠.’ \wj* 
\p  
\v 7 \wj “Ya̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠, odi a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ma̠a̠, ‘Onon o̠nyi̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠. Itue ta̠ ogigh i̠na, sa̠ i̠di̠ar ad̠i̠a d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ a̠ten iya̠ i̠yar.’ \wj* 
\v 8 \wj Sa̠ awa ipuom o̠nyi̠ bho̠, sa̠ igigh i̠na, sa̠ id̠ud̠ur ozu bho̠ irobh d̠a̠ etire.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ku̠a ka̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ere? I̠na ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ aze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom i̠ye̠ ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠eton a̠lei bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo. \wj* 
\v 10 \wj Inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠, ma̠ esi bho̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠a̠: \wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Ekpokpogh ikputu wa̠ iloma̠rutu bho̠ ighel bho̠ \wj* 
\q2 \wj na̠ ra̠ a̠ten e̠ko̠ wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠; \wj* 
\q1  
\v 11 \wj onon abar ola̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠gir,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ amar a̠bhon d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠i̠yar o̠bi̠gh’?” \wj* 
\p  
\v 12 Ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ eloghom ma̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠sidogh bho̠ a̠gboloma̠ awa, sa̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ob̠ol o̠yo̠. Ya̠a̠ awa ighil o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ awa i̠we̠le̠man i̠na iten i̠d̠u̠a. 
\s1 Ipura̠n otua̠ otua̠-ebhugh 
\r (Amatiu 22:15-22; A̠luk 20:20-26) 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ awa ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ bho̠ iruom idi Afarisi na̠ idi ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m ta̠ E̠ro̠d ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠kpati̠ o̠yo̠ ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh abar api̠o̠m.  
\v 14 Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠yar ologhom ma̠ anwa na̠ amar na̠ a̠gir d̠a̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠oyom, sa̠ anwa na̠ okpon d̠o̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠gurumeni abhe̠l opa̠n, sa̠ anwa na̠ a̠bhin ya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠ na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zib̠a̠. Gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar, A̠sora̠n i̠yar otua̠ otua̠-ebhugh\f + \fr 12:14 \fq Otua̠-ebhugh \ft Ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠rom ku̠ku̠m na̠ etua̠.\f* onigha̠ A̠siza̠ ke̠re̠? I̠yar otua̠ bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ i̠yar otua̠ d̠o̠?” 
\p  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom ikoiny d̠awa sa̠ awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin udin ere na̠ o̠kpati̠ ami̠? Ibhine ma̠ a̠dinari̠ ma̠ eru ami̠ ta̠ abi̠gh.” \wj* 
\v 16 Sa̠ awa ibhin a̠dinari̠ bho̠ iruom i̠na, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj “Onon ka̠ a̠misigh ta̠ a̠nyen, sa̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ a̠nyen d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠?” \wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ita̠ A̠siza̠.” 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ku̠a bha̠, inigha̠ ma̠ A̠siza̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ A̠siza̠, ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ita̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” \wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ d̠a̠ ebul awo̠ran d̠o̠yo̠. 
\s1 Ipura̠n wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠  //  ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 22:23-33; A̠luk 20:27-40) 
\p  
\v 18 Ogbo Asadusi ya̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh od̠i bho̠, i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s epura̠n ma̠a̠,  
\v 19 “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, A̠mozizi age̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar ma̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ umor o̠ni̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ad̠u̠a, ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠, ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ani̠ umor bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ amar anwi̠i̠ny a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠.\x - \xo 12:19 \xt Oloko 25:5\x* 
\v 20 I̠se̠n bha̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rumor e̠ro̠; sa̠ okei bho̠ a̠bhin ani̠ ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ sa̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ani̠ bho̠ ad̠u̠a.  
\v 21 Sa̠ oleghemeni i̠wal umor bho̠ a̠bhin ani̠ bho̠, i̠na eka̠ na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ sa̠ a̠mugh. Obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ wa̠leghemeni i̠sar umor bho̠.  
\v 22 A̠mite ma̠ o̠ku̠a oku̠a tu̠tu̠n sa̠ eb̠la̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rumor ya̠ ibhin ani̠ bho̠ imugughu, i̠mar d̠o̠ bebina̠ ekpo o̠nyi̠. Ekunuguma̠ bho̠ sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠mugh nyen.  
\v 23 Igiel ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ ka̠, ani̠ bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ani̠ ta̠ a̠nyen, d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ ani̠ bho̠ na̠ awal eb̠la̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rumor bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ta̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠ o̠pi̠e, ebula̠ agu̠o̠ inyin u̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ ratu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠? \wj* 
\v 25 \wj Igiel imumugh bho̠ ta̠ eb̠egina̠, awa ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny. Awa ko obhinogh d̠o̠ ma̠ anwani̠, sa̠ ko onigha̠nom d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠nyan anwi̠i̠ny nyen. \wj* 
\v 26 \wj Iya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ta̠ eb̠egina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠, inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire ta̠ A̠mozizi ma̠ asu̠gbagba ed̠um bho̠ ma̠ iya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na bho̠ ke̠re̠? Ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Ebraham, na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Azi̠ki̠, na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠.’ \wj* 
\v 27 \wj I̠na A̠zib̠a̠ imumugh d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na ola̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um. Inyin o̠mar o̠ru̠ru̠an o̠pi̠e̠!” \wj* 
\s1 Oloko wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 22:34-40; A̠luk 10:25-28) 
\p  
\v 28 Odi o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ amu̠gho̠n i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an d̠awa, sa̠ abi̠gh ma̠ I̠na amar awo̠ran awa, sa̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Eb̠la̠ roloko bho̠ ka̠ oken a̠lei abar a̠pu?”  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Onon wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠: ‘I̠nagha, E Izre̠l! Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠i̠yar, i̠na ku̠ku̠m Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 30 \wj Bhine ma̠ eb̠la̠ ekpo ologi d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ eloghoma̠n ozu d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an ologi d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mi̠ d̠oyom, ma̠ a̠tula̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom.’ \wj* 
\v 31 \wj Oleghemeni i̠wal bho̠, bha̠ onon: ‘Tula̠ne ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ aka d̠oyom bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa itula̠n ozu d̠oyom bho̠.’ Oloko ola̠ a̠pu ma̠ i̠nye̠n bo̠.” \wj* 
\v 32 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Anwa amar agba ma̠ iya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠. Onin A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m od̠i, opa̠n bo̠, a̠ten i̠na.  
\v 33 Sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠bhin eb̠la̠ ekpo ologi d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an ologi d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mi̠ d̠oyom a̠tula̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom. Sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠tula̠n o̠ni̠ etua̠n d̠oyom ma̠ agu̠o̠ ozu d̠oyom, a̠lei abar a̠pu ma̠ obhin i̠nam o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ na̠ ipa̠n ralu̠kpe̠.”  
\v 34 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh ma̠a̠ i̠na amar awo̠ran bho̠, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ osigima̠ mu nyam.” \wj* Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠ne ma̠ opita̠ opura̠n abar na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. 
\s1 Akrai̠st ka̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ a̠nyen? 
\p  
\v 35 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, \wj “Ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ edin ere na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠ Witenemeni bho̠ ma̠a̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi? \wj* 
\v 36 \wj E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ta̠ A̠devidi na̠ agu̠o̠ agba ma̠a̠, \wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠: \wj* 
\q2 \wj “Ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠\wj* 
\q1 \wj tu̠tu̠n ami̠ ta̠ a̠guri ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠oyom \wj* 
\q2 \wj d̠a̠ ekpukpu a̠sike d̠oyom.” ’\wj* 
\m  
\v 37 \wj A̠devidi na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠bhelegi i̠na ma̠ ‘Wa̠nwuna̠.’ O̠ku̠a ka̠ I̠na aro̠ eka̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠?” \wj* 
\p Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ibhin a̠libhon ologi i̠nagha ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s akparame̠ni̠ a̠kikiom a̠gboloma̠  //  ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 23:36; A̠luk 20:45-47) 
\p  
\v 38 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠. Awa iba̠ra̠ ma̠ opa̠n obura̠ ibom isosora̠n rakapa, sa̠ iba̠ra̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom obhin d̠a̠ ozuruna̠ eghoi obheleguma̠ awa d̠a̠ regbolom a̠b̠ua̠, \wj* 
\v 39 \wj sekina̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ra̠dila̠de edim d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠risisi edim d̠a̠ ro̠d̠e̠. \wj* 
\v 40 \wj Awa na̠ eponoma̠ ma̠ rekpukele anwani̠ na̠ e̠wo̠ro̠gh i̠di̠ar, sa̠ awa na̠ esiseiny iwewegh ra̠siseiny b̠o̠ka̠ olelegi awa. Awa ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ ibom ebhum ase̠.” \wj* 
\s1 Okpoki ali̠se̠bh ta̠ ekpukele ani̠ bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 21:1-4) 
\p  
\v 41 A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de a̠sumogha̠n igba̠ alu̠kpe̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠kpon agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom na̠ ebhin na̠ e̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ ikpoki ali̠se̠bh d̠awa bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh ka̠ a̠d̠izo aru̠lala na̠ e̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠b̠utu ikpoki d̠a̠ ologi.  
\v 42 Sa̠ odi onyigoiny ekpukele ani̠\f + \fr 12:42 \fq Ekpukele ani̠: \ft Ani̠ ola̠ owolom na̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ad̠u̠a\f*, agi̠ ka̠ alo̠gh i̠wal i̠gbara ikpoki ako̠pa\f + \fr 12:42 \fq Ako̠pa: \ft Abar ola̠ akpar ka̠ okurogh, ola̠ a̠nwunom obhel bho̠, ibhin gha̠n i̠le̠m ikpoki na̠ ipa̠n i̠di̠ar o̠le̠m\f*, ya̠ ilei ape̠ni̠.  
\v 43 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ igba̠ bho̠, onyigoiny ekpukele ani̠ onon alo̠gh a̠pu. \wj* 
\v 44 \wj Ezin bho̠, eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n na̠ ibom e̠li̠la d̠awa, wa̠ a̠ru, ape̠to̠n o̠nyi̠ esi d̠a̠ e̠li̠la d̠o̠yo̠ alo̠gh. Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ologi igoiny d̠o̠yo̠, i̠na a̠kpukpu ma̠ eb̠la̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠ alo̠gh.” \wj* 
\c 13  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ ma̠ ta̠ ob̠ogion otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:1-2; A̠luk 21:5-6) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Kpone! A̠libhon ikputu bho̠ na̠ a̠rutu bho̠!”  
\v 2 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh ibom a̠rutu i̠nye̠n? Bebina̠ ikputu ola̠ ta̠ a̠sughonom i̠se̠n ola̠ odi ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ ta̠ odi bo̠, ola̠ ko ob̠ogion d̠o̠ bo̠.” \wj* 
\s1 I̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh na̠ okpon ogurumeni 
\r (Amatiu 24:3-14; A̠luk 21:7-19) 
\p  
\v 3 A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ anyu̠ Igu Oliv d̠a̠ esumogha̠n Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ A̠puta̠, na̠ A̠zemsi, na̠ Azo̠n, na̠ Anduru, iru ra̠ ipura̠n i̠na d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ma̠a̠,  
\v 4 “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar, i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ka̠ ta̠ emite ma̠ a̠kere obhel? Sa̠ i̠yar ta̠ obhin a̠kere a̠d̠ien elegh ologhom ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ etua̠n omite?” 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ko ogelemeni d̠o̠ inyin. \wj* 
\v 6 \wj A̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhin a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ eru ra̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ i̠na!’ sa̠ awa ta̠ egelemeni ma̠ a̠d̠izo ogbo. \wj* 
\v 7 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ko okperenuma̠ ma̠ igiel inyin u̠mu̠gho̠n oghur re̠gham na̠ i̠mu̠mu̠gho̠n re̠gham. O̠kpo̠ ya̠ o̠ku̠a ta̠ emite, ya̠a̠ o̠ku̠a na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ na̠ ate̠i̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ebhugh ta̠ a̠wia̠n ebhugh, sa̠ a̠de e̠ma ta̠ a̠wia̠n a̠de e̠ma. Ra̠de ta̠ eb̠ob̠omia̠n kesi kesi, sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n ta̠ a̠sor. Ya̠a̠, i̠nye̠n ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r o̠ke̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ma̠ agu̠o̠ iguna̠ i̠mara. \wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “Be̠le̠ni̠, i̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠. Ta̠ ob̠ologh inyin obhin o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ a̠rutu osobh ase̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma bho̠ na̠ d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala A̠zu, sa̠ ta̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh inyin. Sa̠ ta̠ o̠marame̠ni̠ inyin d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogbo aru̠mu̠ ebhugh na̠ aru̠lala e̠ma d̠a̠ ebula̠ ami̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠gba ami̠ onigha̠ awa. \wj* 
\v 10 \wj Ta̠ od̠ia̠ o̠gba nyen ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ omutiom onigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠dede. \wj* 
\v 11 \wj Sa̠ igiel ubhin inyin u̠gi̠o̠m awa, o̠ni̠ ko od̠ia̠ ma̠ e̠ku̠nu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ obhin o̠gba o̠nu̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar iya̠ unigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ ogbo obhel bha̠. Ezin bho̠, inyin d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ta̠ e̠gba bho̠, ya̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\p  
\v 12 \wj “Umor ta̠ a̠wol umor ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogigh, sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ ta̠ a̠wol o̠nyi̠, sa̠ anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ ewia̠n ronweni na̠ ro̠we̠de̠ ma̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ awa. \wj* 
\v 13 \wj Sa̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ta̠ asu̠a inyin d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ne tu̠tu̠n ka̠ a̠kunugiom bho̠, bha̠ oten. \wj* 
\s1 Obom ali̠gam ozu bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:15-28; A̠luk 21:20-24) 
\p  
\v 14 \wj “Igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh ‘ka̠ ibom i̠pi̠o̠gho̠m wa̠ na̠ api̠e̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠’ na̠ amara ma̠ esi bho̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠ro̠ bho̠, (bha̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠sen bho̠ amu̠gho̠nyan), o̠ni̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠ bho̠ a̠kpo ma̠ eghil ad̠u̠a agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh rigu bho̠. \wj*\x - \xo 13:14 \xt Adan 9:17; 11:31; 12:11\x* 
\v 15 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu osor d̠o̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠bhin abar d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mite. \wj* 
\v 16 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ o̠si̠ omula̠ d̠o̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin akapa anyu̠ d̠o̠yo̠. \wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ekulom anwani̠ a̠rughun na̠ iya̠ anwi̠i̠ny od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ e̠mam d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠ye̠. \wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ya̠a̠, isiseinye ma̠ o̠kpo̠ i̠nye̠n omite d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel a̠d̠igho. \wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ezin bho̠, a̠d̠ien egbika̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠ye̠ ta̠ omite d̠o̠ ka̠ d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton o̠le̠me̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ale̠m bho̠ tu̠tu̠n ra̠ ate̠i̠ i̠se̠n, sa̠ ka̠ omula̠ mu emite. \wj* 
\p  
\v 20 \wj “Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ okperemeni d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel bho̠, bha̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠miza̠n bo̠. O̠ku̠a eka̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ aso̠n a̠bhin bho̠, bha̠ i̠na na̠ a̠kperemeni ma̠ obhel bho̠. \wj* 
\v 21 \wj Sa̠ d̠a̠ obhel obha̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ a̠ru ra̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Ikpone! Akrai̠st od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n!’ bo̠d̠o̠, ‘Ikpone! I̠na od̠i ma̠ ebha̠,’ o̠ni̠ ko oma̠ra̠. \wj* 
\v 22 \wj Rakrai̠st igunugha̠ na̠ a̠riwil igunugha̠ ta̠ emite eru ra̠ egir ilologia̠n, sa̠ ta̠ emutioghom relegh ya̠ obhin ogelemeni a̠nwunom, ku̠gba ma̠ a̠b̠ur, bha̠ ogbo iya̠ na̠ o̠so̠n bho̠ nyen. \wj* 
\v 23 \wj Ikpona̠ o! Ami̠ nà̠ agba kabar kabar a̠nigha̠ inyin i̠se̠n kisa̠ obhel bho̠ ta̠ a̠lei. \wj* 
\s1 Eruoma̠ ta̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:29-31; A̠luk 21:25-28) 
\p  
\v 24 \wj “D̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠ye̠, ma̠ igiel ali̠gam a̠ruzu bho̠ na̠ eten,\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘sa̠ ogogo bho̠ ta̠ azu̠, \wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ uwetire bho̠ ko o̠mu̠ mu̠; \wj* 
\q1  
\v 25 \wj sa̠ i̠ni̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny emeleghu, \wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ ra̠limon e̠nai̠ny ta̠ enyegia̠n.’ \wj* 
\p  
\v 26 \wj “Sa̠ d̠a̠ obhel obha̠, a̠nwunom ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ka̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ na̠ a̠ru na̠ ibom a̠limon na̠ isosorogia̠n.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ruom itileduom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ okokod̠i ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ aso̠n bho̠, d̠a̠ inya̠ re̠ku̠l e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ob̠eton d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠gbaki̠ a̠de ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ obhubhulom.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh oriren A̠fig bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:32-35; A̠luk 21:29-33) 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “I̠se̠n, ibhine ma̠ a̠sidogh oriren a̠fig\wj*\f + \fr 13:28 \fq A̠fig: \ft Odi ad̠ien oriren d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l, ola̠ na̠ a̠guna̠ ma̠ a̠d̠igho, sa̠ i̠mu̠n na̠ ra̠lele d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠mu̠r na̠ emite ma̠ igiel a̠kozogh na̠ a̠ru.\f*\wj bho̠ ma̠ e̠tu̠ghan abar. Igiel i̠gha d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ edugh sa̠ i̠mu̠nu̠mu̠n bho̠ na̠ e̠mu̠r na̠ emite, bha̠ inyin na̠ ologhom ma̠ a̠kozogh na̠ a̠tua̠n. \wj* 
\v 29 \wj Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh ka̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ emite, bha̠ iloghome ma̠a̠, na̠ a̠tua̠n, na̠ a̠misi d̠a̠ o̠nu̠otu.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, amu̠m onon ko oten d̠o̠ kisa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj A̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ny ta̠ eten e̠d̠u̠a, ya̠a̠ ikpo a̠fugh d̠ami̠ ko oten d̠o̠ na̠ oten e̠d̠u̠a.\wj* 
\s1 O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom a̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ obhel bho̠ bo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:36-44) 
\p  
\v 32 \wj “I̠se̠n, iya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bo̠d̠o̠ obhel bho̠, bebina̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom bo̠, a̠d̠igh itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, O̠nyi̠ bho̠ eka̠, a̠sigimeni ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 33 \wj Ikpona̠! Igone! Ezin bho̠ inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel bho̠ ekunuguma̠ obhel bho̠ ta̠ aro̠.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠, sa̠ awe̠le̠man eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ igoni d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ okponom, o̠ni̠no̠ o̠ni̠no̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ ta̠ a̠gir, sa̠ a̠ruom okponomotu\wj*\f + \fr 13:34 \ft Okponomotu: O̠ni̠ ipoiny ola̠ na̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠otu na̠ a̠gon.\f*\wj bho̠ ma̠a̠, aro̠ ma̠ omom a̠gon.\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, igone, ezin bho̠ inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel bho̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru. Ta̠ a̠rue aro̠ ma̠ a̠dule, bo̠d̠o̠ egum a̠d̠io, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ obhel olobhiri e̠nu̠r na̠ alal, bo̠d̠o̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠. \wj* 
\v 36 \wj Ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ka̠ a̠ru ma̠ awai̠, i̠na o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ anwa na̠ a̠kod̠u. \wj* 
\v 37 \wj Sa̠ abar wa̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin bho̠, bha̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠. ‘Igone!’ ” \wj* 
\c 14  
\s1 Imimia̠n Ogigh A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:1-5; A̠luk 22:1-2; Azo̠n 11:45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 I̠se̠n bha̠ i̠wal a̠d̠a̠ma̠ isugho ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠ sekina̠ E̠yal Abe̠re̠di̠ ya̠ Owubh d̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ imimia̠n agu̠o̠ awa ta̠ ebhin ikoiny eb̠ol A̠zizo̠s egigh.  
\v 2 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠gba ma̠a̠, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ e̠yal bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ bha̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ esoroni ma̠ elobhiri. 
\s1 Uwuri ma̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:1; 14:3-9; Azo̠n 12:1-8) 
\p  
\v 3 I̠se̠n, bha̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠i d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠. Sa̠ odi ani̠ a̠bhin ololo alabasta ola̠ u̠lo̠gh a̠ga̠i amu̠nu̠ Aspai̠knad\f + \fr 14:3 \ft Aspai̠knad: 
\fp \ft Amu̠nu̠ iya̠ na̠ emite d̠a̠ anad. Anad bha̠ oriren ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠.\f* obom a̠b̠ua̠ a̠ru. Sa̠ a̠b̠om o̠nu̠no̠nu̠ ololo bho̠ a̠zugioghom amu̠nu̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 4 Sa̠ idi ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ i̠ki̠kai̠ngha, sa̠ odi a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ma̠a̠, “I̠na a̠din ere na̠ a̠robh amu̠nu̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ bho̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a?  
\v 5 Onon sa̠ ka̠ urue owol opeleni ma̠ od̠ua̠l e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh a̠dinari̠\f + \fr 14:5 \ft A̠dinari̠: Onin a̠dinari̠ bha̠ ikpoki ogir e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ d̠a̠ obhel obha̠.\f* (300) obhin o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠.” Sa̠ awa i̠li̠o̠m ani̠ bho̠ ma̠ ibom.  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠we̠le̠ ma̠ ani̠ bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠. Inyin udin ere na̠ onigha̠ i̠na ma̠ ali̠gam a̠luzu? I̠na na̠ a̠gir ob̠eb̠i abar a̠nigha̠ ami̠. \wj* 
\v 7 \wj Ronyigoiny bho̠ sa̠ od̠i na̠ inyin eb̠la̠ obhel, inyin ta̠ orue o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ awa kere kere obhel ola̠ a̠d̠igh inyin ologi. Ya̠a̠ ami̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ na̠ inyin eb̠la̠ obhel. \wj* 
\v 8 \wj I̠na a̠gir abar wa̠ i̠na a̠rue ma̠ ogir bho̠, ma̠ od̠ia̠ ozuom ami̠ amu̠nu̠ iya̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man ozu d̠ami̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠ma̠d̠i. \wj* 
\v 9 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, kesi kesi ola̠ ta̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠ebi̠ asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ta̠ o̠gba nyen, ogir onon wa̠ ani̠ onon a̠gir bho̠, ma̠ obhin o̠ru̠ru̠an o̠yo̠.” \wj* 
\s1 A̠ma̠ra̠nua̠n ta̠ A̠zuda̠s wa̠ owol A̠zizo̠s bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:14-16; A̠luk 22:3-6) 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ A̠zuda̠s I̠skari̠o̠t, odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠, a̠ten agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠wol A̠zizo̠s a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 11 Sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ ibhon ologi ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n ya̠ i̠na agba bho̠, sa̠ igua̠n onigha̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠ ikpoki. Ob̠eton d̠a̠ obhel obha̠ sa̠ A̠zuda̠s abho̠ro̠gh e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ ta̠ a̠sora̠n owol A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠e ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten na̠ ogbo ogir do̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:17-25; A̠luk 22:7-14; Azo̠n 13:21-30) 
\p  
\v 12 D̠a̠ o̠pu̠r a̠d̠a̠ma̠ E̠yal Abe̠re̠di̠ wa̠ Owubh d̠o̠ bho̠, a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ na̠ ogigh o̠nyi̠ o̠nana E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠, sa̠ ogbo ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na, ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “A̠kere esi wa̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan i̠yar o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man osisa̠n oyom ma̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠?” 
\m  
\v 13 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom i̠wal ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh od̠i o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rol izoko amu̠m, i̠tu̠o̠no̠me̠ i̠na. \wj* 
\v 14 \wj Sa̠ i̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu wa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠igh bho̠ ma̠a̠: ‘O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠: oken e̠kpe̠ isuloma̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ogbo ogir d̠ami̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠?’ \wj* 
\v 15 \wj Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ atu̠o̠m a̠leriom inyin obom e̠kpe̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu a̠b̠ekei bho̠, ola̠ na̠ o̠mar oburi oguri, ma̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠man i̠se̠ ma̠ esisa̠n i̠yar.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠tu̠ghu̠man ed̠ia̠n Opel Oten bho̠.  
\v 17 Ate̠i̠ a̠dule, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ iten i̠gi̠.  
\v 18 Agu̠o̠ awa od̠i d̠a̠ akpata od̠e na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, odi o̠ni̠ inyin wa̠ na̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠d̠e bho̠, ta̠ a̠wol ami̠.”\wj* 
\v 19 Sa̠ awa id̠igh i̠ku̠nu̠ ma̠ ibom, sa̠ o̠ni̠ o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ ake̠ ma̠ opura̠n o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ ke̠re̠?”  
\v 20 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Odi o̠ni̠ inyin d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠, wa̠ na̠ a̠tiom d̠a̠ onin e̠kpa ed̠ia̠n na̠ ami̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠mugh agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ ogboloma̠ ina̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠wol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ bho̠. Ka̠ ibhon a̠pu ma̠ u̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ obha̠!”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠mutiom od̠e ed̠ia̠n e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:26-30; A̠luk 22:14-20; 1 Ako̠ri̠nt 11:23-25) 
\p  
\v 22 D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ ed̠e bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin abe̠re̠di̠ a̠tutumeni, sa̠ a̠puiny a̠nigha̠ awa sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ibhine, onon ozu d̠ami̠ wa̠ na̠ onigha̠ inyin bho̠.”\wj* 
\v 23 Sa̠ a̠bhin okpa̠ko a̠min, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ali̠se̠bh, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ awa, sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa ibhin i̠d̠a.  
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Onon asi̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ omom i̠zo̠ bho̠, wa̠ uzu, ma̠ o̠ta eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom o̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh. \wj* 
\v 25 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ob̠eton i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ami̠ ko o̠d̠a mu̠ ma̠ a̠min itu a̠grep tu̠tu̠n a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ ad̠a ma̠ omom bho̠ d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.”\wj* 
\m  
\v 26 Sa̠ awa i̠mo̠r aso̠r, sa̠ i̠d̠u̠a i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Igu Roliv. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ ma̠ A̠puta̠ ta̠ aku̠a i̠na 
\r (Amatiu 26:31-35; A̠luk 22:31-34; Azo̠n 13:36-38) 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ eb̠la̠ inyin ta̠ oghel A̠zib̠a̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: \wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Ami̠ ta̠ agu̠r okponom ro̠nana bho̠ a̠teb̠eli, \wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ o̠lo̠gh ro̠nana bho̠ ta̠ e̠sasaragi̠an.’ \wj*\x - \xo 14:27 \xt Azak 13:7\x* 
\v 28 \wj Ya̠a̠, igiel ami̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili ka̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ inyin.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠puta̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom i̠we̠le̠man anwa iten i̠d̠u̠a eka̠, ami̠ ko oghil ani̠ d̠o̠ ad̠u̠a.” 
\p  
\v 30 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, a̠d̠ugula̠n onon, kisa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r ta̠ alal i̠wal igiel, anwa ta̠ aku̠a ami̠ ma̠ i̠sar igiel, ma̠a̠ anwa na̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ A̠puta̠ akparame̠ni̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ anwa a̠mugh eka̠, ami̠ ko o̠ku̠a d̠o̠ nyam.” Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom iyed̠i ifugh ani̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a. 
\s1 A̠siseiny ta̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ Age̠tse̠mane̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:36-46; A̠luk 22:39-46) 
\p  
\v 32 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan do̠yo̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ esi ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Age̠tse̠mane̠, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ma̠ i̠se̠n, ya̠ ami̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠siseiny.”\wj* 
\v 33 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin A̠puta̠ na̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n ab̠aragu̠ma i̠na, sa̠ ibom asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an na̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ ra̠ id̠igh i̠na. 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Eloghoma̠n ozu d̠ami̠ na̠ ku̠nu̠ ma̠ ibom, aro̠ ka̠ omugh a̠sugho. I̠ro̠ ma̠ omom ma̠ i̠se̠n.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠kara ka̠ a̠mel a̠b̠obhia̠n d̠a̠ a̠de, sa̠ a̠siseiny ma̠a̠, ta̠ a̠b̠ur nab̠o̠, obhel onon ka̠ iten ad̠u̠a d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 36 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “Ada, O̠we̠de̠, anwa ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir kabar kabar, si̠ghe̠ ma̠ okpa̠ko onon d̠a̠ ozu d̠ami̠. Ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ku d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠ami̠, aro̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠oyom.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ awa, sa̠ abi̠gh ma̠ awa na̠ ekod̠u, sa̠ a̠pura̠n A̠puta̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Asai̠mo̠n, anwa na̠ a̠kod̠u ke̠re̠? Kpo̠ruzu ma̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ omom bebina̠ o̠nyi̠ obhel. \wj* 
\v 38 \wj I̠ro̠ ma̠ omom ma̠ esiseiny b̠o̠ka̠ inyin umel d̠o̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ ad̠agi̠an. Na̠ ebhir e̠mu̠gh bho̠, ya̠a̠ ozu bho̠ na̠ a̠dugh.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ i̠na a̠puta̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠siseiny onin agu̠o̠ bho̠.  
\v 40 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ a̠ru ra̠ abi̠gh ma̠ awa na̠ ekod̠u eten, ezin bho̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠awa na̠ e̠mu̠mo̠r ibom ma̠ ola̠ awa iloghom mu ma̠ abar ola̠ o̠wo̠ran o̠yo̠.  
\v 41 A̠zizo̠s a̠ru ma̠ oleghemeni i̠sar igiel bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “Inyin od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ okod̠u na̠ osira̠ ma̠ epobh ke̠re̠? Na̠ a̠bhon! Obhel wa̠ u̠to̠ uguri bho̠ na̠ a̠lei. Ikpone, na̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh. \wj* 
\v 42 \wj Ib̠egina̠! Id̠ighi ta̠ oten o̠gi̠. O̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠wol ami̠ bho̠ od̠i d̠a̠ aka.” \wj* 
\s1 Owol na̠ ob̠ol A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:47-56; A̠luk 22:47-53; Azo̠n 18:3-12) 
\p  
\v 43 A̠zizo̠s od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh, sa̠ A̠zuda̠s odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ a̠ru na̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠kpanaki̠an ralapa ogidi na̠ re̠b̠am, iya̠ aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ iruom.  
\v 44 I̠se̠n, o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠wol i̠na bho̠ na̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ api̠pi̠o̠bh bho̠ bha̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠, ib̠ole i̠na ma̠ esibhom e̠kparame̠ni̠.”  
\v 45 Sa̠ A̠zuda̠s a̠ru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠,” sa̠ api̠pi̠o̠bh i̠na.  
\v 46 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ iru ra̠ ipuom A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ agu̠o̠, sa̠ ib̠ol i̠na, isibhom i̠kparame̠ni̠.  
\v 47 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ etua̠n, abho̠ro̠n alapa ogidi d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ a̠sobh a̠to ta̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ a̠b̠uton.  
\v 48 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n o̠go̠ ebhugh ke̠re̠, ma̠ ola̠ inyin ubhin alapa a̠rigidi na̠ re̠b̠am uru ra̠ ob̠ol ami̠?\wj* 
\v 49 \wj Ka̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ami̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ inyin d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ inyin ub̠ol d̠o̠ ami̠. Ya̠a̠, eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ emite ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠.” \wj* 
\v 50 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠we̠le̠ i̠na ighil i̠d̠u̠a. 
\s1 O̠nyi̠ Oyel wa̠ a̠ghil ad̠u̠a bho̠ 
\p  
\v 51 Odi o̠nyi̠ oyel ola̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ani̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠, i̠na alagha ma̠ ososora̠n akapa asi̠ni̠ni̠n ku̠ku̠m. A̠nwunom bho̠ i̠b̠ar na̠ i̠na esibh,  
\v 52 sa̠ i̠na a̠gbugbugha̠ awe̠le̠ ma̠ ososora̠n akapa asi̠ni̠ni̠n bho̠ a̠ghil ad̠u̠a ma̠ e̠dab̠a. 
\s1 Ubhin A̠zizo̠s o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ I̠gada Osobh Ase̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:57-68; A̠luk 22:54-55,63-71; Azo̠n 18:13-14,19-24) 
\p  
\v 53 Sa̠ awa ibhin A̠zizo̠s i̠gi̠o̠m we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ aru̠mu̠ okur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ ikokod̠ia̠n.  
\v 54 Sa̠ A̠puta̠ aro̠ ma̠ egbeny atu̠o̠no̠m i̠na tu̠tu̠n ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ogigo i̠gada ase̠ ta̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠. Sa̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de a̠sumogha̠n e̠banya bho̠ na̠ amu̠ga.  
\v 55 I̠se̠ sa̠ ibom rokur bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ Ogbo Osobh Ase̠ A̠zu bho̠ i̠bho̠ro̠ghan a̠nwunom ya̠ ta̠ e̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ igunugha̠ eb̠ologiom A̠zizo̠s, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ ebhin esobh ase̠ ebhumeni i̠na egigh, ya̠a̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠.  
\v 56 A̠d̠izo ronyob̠a̠ igunugha̠ emite ra̠ e̠gba ma̠ o̠nu̠ eb̠ologiom i̠na, ya̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠awa id̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ onin.  
\v 57 Sa̠ idi ronyob̠a̠ imite, sa̠ i̠gba ma̠ igunugha̠ ib̠ologiom i̠na ma̠a̠:  
\v 58 “I̠yar u̠mo̠gho̠n ka̠ o̠ni̠ onon a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠b̠ogion Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ a̠lo bho̠, sa̠ d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠lo ma̠ opa̠n ola̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ olo.’ ”  
\v 59 Eb̠la̠ i̠se̠ eka̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ awa i̠gba ib̠ologiom A̠zizo̠s bho̠ id̠igh d̠o̠ onin. 
\p  
\v 60 Sa̠ We̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ a̠rile a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa a̠pura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ o̠wo̠ran d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? Onon ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien abar ola̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ ob̠ologiom anwa?”  
\v 61 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s aro̠ b̠u̠b̠o̠m, na̠ o̠wo̠ran d̠o̠ ma̠ abar. Sa̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ a̠puta̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa Akrai̠st O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ akpe̠ ma̠ otutumeni bho̠ ke̠re̠?”  
\v 62 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ i̠na. Inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ka̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ agba od̠iom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ A̠limon A̠pu bho̠. Sekina̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ru na̠ ro̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny.”\wj* 
\v 63 Sa̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ ago̠ ma̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ta̠ odin ere o̠bho̠ro̠ghan ipa̠n ronyob̠a̠?”  
\v 64 “I̠bi̠ghe̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠fugh a̠fugh i̠basi̠ na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Inyin u̠bi̠gh eka̠?” Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ api̠o̠gho̠m, akpe̠ ma̠ omugh.”  
\v 65 Sa̠ idi awa i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠si̠ro̠gho̠m o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠gho̠r, sa̠ ibinom a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ib̠orogh i̠na, sa̠ ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠ “Wa̠.” Sa̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ ibhin i̠na ib̠orogh. 
\s1 A̠puta̠ Aku̠a ma̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:69-75; A̠luk 22:56-62; Azo̠n 18:15-18,25-27) 
\p  
\v 66 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ A̠puta̠ od̠i ma̠ agba wa̠ ade̠bh d̠a̠ ologi ogigo bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠nyani̠, ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠,  
\v 67 abi̠gh ka̠ A̠puta̠ na̠ amu̠ga ma̠ anya, sa̠ a̠gbiom a̠kpon i̠na, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa odi o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠ro̠ ani̠ na̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anazare̠t bho̠.”  
\v 68 Sa̠, A̠puta̠ aku̠a a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ anwa na̠ agba bho̠, ami̠ i̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ nyam nyen.” Sa̠ A̠puta̠ a̠mite agi̠ ka̠ amara d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ogigo bho̠, sa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r alal.  
\v 69 Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ abi̠gh i̠na sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ odi d̠a̠ aka bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Onon odi o̠ni̠ awa!”  
\v 70 Sa̠ a̠mula̠ aku̠a. O̠nyi̠ obhel oten, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ aka bho̠ ifugh inigha̠ ma̠ A̠puta̠ ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i anwa odi o̠ni̠ awa, ezin bho̠ anwa ola̠ Agalili.”  
\v 71 O̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ osibhigha̠, ogurugia̠n ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon wa̠ inyin na̠ ofugh ogboloma̠ bho̠!”  
\v 72 I̠se̠ sa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r alal wa̠ a̠leghemeni i̠wal igiel. Sa̠ A̠puta̠ aru̠ru̠an agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Kisa̠ e̠nu̠r ta̠ alal i̠wal igiel, anwa ta̠ aku̠a ami̠ ma̠ i̠sar igiel” \wj* Sa̠ A̠puta̠ aku̠ru̠ru̠ a̠sorogi ma̠ izin. 
\c 15  
\s1 Ubhin A̠zizo̠s O̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Apai̠let 
\r (Amatiu 27:1,2,11-14; A̠luk 23:1-5; Azo̠n 18:28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, d̠a̠ obom ame̠ghe̠le̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ okur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠, na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko, na̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo i̠gada ase̠ bho̠ imimia̠n iya̠ ogir ogboloma̠ A̠zizo̠s. Sa̠ i̠bhad̠i̠ i̠na, irileghom i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Apai̠let.  
\v 2 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠: “Anwa o̠li̠le̠ma A̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠ ke̠re̠?” Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa na̠ agba.”\wj* 
\v 3 Sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ okur bho̠ i̠gba ma̠ a̠d̠izo o̠kpo̠ ib̠ologiom i̠na.  
\v 4 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠mula̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Abar ola̠ anwa inwuna̠ ma̠ o̠wo̠ran bo̠ ke̠re̠? Mu̠gho̠ne̠ ma̠ a̠d̠izo riku ya̠ uler anwa bho̠!”  
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ omula̠ d̠o̠ awo̠ran abar, ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh Apai̠let ilologia̠n. 
\s1 Usobh ase̠ omugh obhumeni ma̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 27:15-26; A̠luk 23:3-25; Azo̠n 18:28-39) 
\p  
\v 6 Kigiel kigiel ola̠ E̠yal Opel Oten a̠sor, bha̠ na̠ omutiom gha̠n d̠a̠ ikoli ma̠ onin o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ipuru.  
\v 7 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Abarabas, ola̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ipa̠n ogbo a̠wia̠n a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ igigh o̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ e̠ma bho̠ na̠ a̠bhighibhighi bho̠, aro̠ d̠a̠ ikoli.  
\v 8 Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ opuru agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ ogir agu̠o̠ na̠ ogir gha̠n bho̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ Apai̠let awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh ma̠ ami̠ imutiom o̠li̠le̠ma A̠zu bho̠ inigha̠ inyin ke̠re̠?”  
\v 10 Ezin bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ okur bho̠ ibhin d̠a̠ egbugbo ologi eb̠ol i̠na.  
\v 11 Ya̠a̠, ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ itumugiom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ opuru agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ omutiom Abarabas onigha̠ awa.  
\v 12 Sa̠, Apai̠let a̠puta̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh ma̠ ami̠ igir ere igboloma̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ inyin na̠ obhelegi ma̠ o̠li̠le̠ma A̠zu bho̠?”  
\v 13 Sa̠ awa ipita̠ i̠ko̠ro̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠du̠e̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠gigh!”  
\v 14 Ya̠a̠, Apai̠let a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere? I̠na a̠gir ere api̠e̠?” Sa̠ awa imula̠ i̠lo̠gh e̠mi̠ imulughu ma̠a̠, “Du̠e̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠gigh!”  
\v 15 Od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ ologi a̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ ab̠al, sa̠ Apai̠let a̠mutiom Abarabas a̠nigha̠ awa. Sa̠ a̠ruom ma̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ a̠b̠eton a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ o̠du̠ ogigh. 
\s1 Ogbo E̠gham I̠ki̠ri̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 27:27-31; Azo̠n 19:2-3) 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ ogbo e̠gham bho̠ ibhin A̠zizo̠s i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ otu a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ta̠ we̠mu̠ ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ ikokod̠i ma̠ eb̠la̠ odi ebu ogbo e̠gham\f + \fr 15:16 \ft Ebu onon bho̠ bha̠ ebu o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala ogbo e̠gham (600).\f* bho̠.  
\v 17 Sa̠ iburi i̠na ma̠ ososora̠n akapa ozu a̠dolo, sa̠ ilo ma̠ eghoi ib̠ub̠ulom izuom i̠na.  
\v 18 Sa̠ awa i̠ke̠ ma̠ obhelegima̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “E O̠li̠le̠ma A̠zu! I̠yar na̠ obheleguma̠ nyam o!”  
\v 19 Sa̠ ibhin okpeti ib̠orogh e̠mu̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠si̠ro̠gho̠m i̠na ma̠ i̠gho̠r, sa̠ ikpud̠ia̠n i̠na izuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi.  
\v 20 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na e̠we̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠ko̠gi̠o̠n ibura̠ ozu a̠dolo bho̠, sa̠ inwe i̠lo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ irileghom i̠na i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ ka̠ o̠du̠ o̠yo̠ ogigh. 
\s1 U̠du̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s Ogigh 
\r (Amatiu 27:32-44; A̠luk 23:26-43; Azo̠n 19:17-27) 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ awa i̠mi̠nana ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ A̠sirin ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Asai̠mo̠n, o̠we̠de̠ ta̠ Ale̠gzanda na̠ A̠rufo̠si̠, d̠a̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠sala na̠ a̠ru, sa̠ iponoma̠ i̠na ma̠ orol e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 22 Sa̠ inuoghom A̠zizo̠s i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Ago̠lgo̠ta (a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, “Esi okpokpo e̠mu̠.”)  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠gu̠a ma̠ amaya d̠a̠ a̠min inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠d̠a, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ko ologhoma̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ali̠gam, ya̠ i̠na na̠ o̠d̠a d̠o̠.  
\v 24 Sa̠ ogbo e̠gham bho̠ i̠du̠ i̠na d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠. Sa̠ awa irobh okob̠a̠ ibhin i̠ru̠gi̠an ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 25 I̠du̠ i̠na d̠a̠ esugho o̠wal-obhel ma̠ asi̠ro̠.  
\v 26 Sa̠ i̠ge̠ ma̠ iku ase̠ d̠o̠yo̠ i̠du̠o̠m d̠a̠ anyu̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠ ma̠a̠: “O̠LI̠LE̠MA A̠NWUNOM A̠ZU BHO̠.”  
\v 27 Sa̠ i̠du̠ nyen i̠wal i̠bho̠ru̠bho̠ru̠ aru̠gba, odi d̠a̠ agba od̠iom d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ uwed̠i d̠a̠ okiel. [ 
\v 28 I̠nye̠n imuzoghod̠iom agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠; “U̠wal ani̠ i̠na o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ ogbo id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.”\f + \fr 15:28 \ft Idi robhurugho bho̠ i̠lo̠gh ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠go̠go̠ onon.\f*]  
\v 29 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eten bho̠ i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na izizigha̠ ma̠ aru̠mu̠ d̠awa inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ e̠ka ifugh ma̠a̠, “A̠soroma̠ nyam! Anwa wa̠ i̠gba ma̠ anwa ta̠ a̠rue a̠b̠ogion Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠lo amado̠n d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠.  
\v 30 Tenemeni ma̠ ozu d̠oyom, ma̠ a̠sor d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠ ma̠ a̠ru!”  
\v 31 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠fugh na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ma̠a̠: “I̠na na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo, ya̠a̠ na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ otenemeni ozu d̠o̠yo̠!  
\v 32 Akrai̠st O̠li̠le̠ma Izre̠l bho̠! I̠se̠n, sore d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠ ma̠ a̠ru, sa̠ i̠yar ta̠ od̠umom anwa!” Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ u̠du̠ na̠ i̠na bho̠ i̠ki̠ri̠ ani̠ i̠na. 
\s1 Omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 27:45-56; A̠luk 23:44-49; Azo̠n 19:28-30) 
\p  
\v 33 O̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠wal-obhel d̠a̠ azai̠ny, sa̠ azi̠m a̠kpegiom eb̠la̠ ebhugh bho̠ tu̠tu̠n ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ i̠sar o̠wal-obhel ma̠ etita̠n.  
\v 34 D̠a̠ i̠sar o̠wal-obhel bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mulughu na̠ obom okoroko ma̠a̠, \wj “E̠lo̠i̠, E̠lo̠i̠, lama sabaktani̠?”\wj* (onon a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠zib̠a̠ d̠ami̠, A̠zib̠a̠ d̠ami̠, anwa idin ere na̠ a̠gin ami̠?”\wj*) 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ idi awa ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “Na̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ I̠lai̠za.”  
\v 36 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ awa a̠ghil ka̠ ato̠ri̠ ma̠ asapu̠ d̠a̠ igheghed̠um a̠min, sa̠ akpu̠o̠m d̠a̠ o̠lo̠ a̠b̠eton a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠d̠a, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “I̠we̠le̠, ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ka̠ I̠lai̠za ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠soroni i̠na.”  
\v 37 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin obom okoroko a̠mulughu, sa̠ ekpo epobh bho̠ a̠sobha̠n.  
\v 38 Sa̠ ukpe wa̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, ake̠ d̠a̠ eb̠o bho̠ agu̠an a̠sor i̠wal a̠bin.  
\v 39 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham\f + \fr 15:39 \ft We̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham onon, bha̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠kponom ogbo e̠gham ya̠ ilei i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100).\f* wa̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ aka a̠sumogha̠n A̠zizo̠s, abi̠gh agu̠o̠ bho̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠mugh bho̠, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, onon O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠!”  
\v 40 Idi anwani̠ e̠ro̠ nyen ma̠ ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ egbeny ekpon. Anwani̠ i̠ye̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠, na̠ A̠meri onweni ta̠ A̠zemsi o̠gbara bho̠ na̠ A̠zosisi\f + \fr 15:40 \ft A̠zosisi onon bho̠, bha̠ opa̠n agu̠o̠ na̠ obhelegi ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠.\f* o̠gbara bho̠, na̠ Asalomi.  
\v 41 Awa i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ enigha̠ i̠na ma̠ obhel bho̠ i̠na aro̠ d̠a̠ Agalili bho̠. A̠d̠izo ipa̠n anwani̠ ya̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠na i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠ e̠ro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠. 
\s1 A̠ma̠d̠i ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 27:57-61; A̠luk 23:50-56; Azo̠n 19:38-42) 
\p  
\v 42 Igiel bho̠ ate̠i̠ a̠dule A̠d̠a̠ma̠ A̠kokod̠ia̠n bho̠, wa̠ i̠b̠ala bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠,  
\v 43 sa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ wa̠ Ari̠mati̠a bho̠, odi o̠ni̠ i̠gada ase̠ bho̠, ola̠ ubhin i̠tu̠o̠m abar ibom, ola̠ na̠ a̠gon irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, akpo̠ ma̠ ologi agi̠ d̠a̠ Apai̠let ka̠ a̠puru ma̠ ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 44 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n Apai̠let ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠mugh ka̠ a̠mugha̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham bho̠ a̠pura̠n ku̠gba ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠mugh ga̠i.  
\v 45 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ Apai̠let na̠ amu̠gho̠n d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ we̠mu̠ e̠gham bho̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu bho̠ ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠.  
\v 46 Sa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ a̠gho ma̠ ukpe asi̠ni̠ni̠n, sa̠ a̠soroni ma̠ egua̠de bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin ukpe bho̠ a̠bhurugi. Sa̠ a̠d̠i i̠na d̠a̠ od̠i ola̠ i̠na a̠b̠u a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠gbo o̠gbi̠o̠ma, sa̠ a̠kikiligi ma̠ o̠gbi̠o̠ma a̠kpegiom od̠i bho̠.  
\v 47 Sa̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠ na̠ A̠meri onweni ta̠ A̠zosisi i̠bi̠gh esi wa̠ ud̠i i̠na bho̠. 
\c 16  
\s1 Ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ Omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 28:1-8; A̠luk 24:1-12; Azo̠n 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠ a̠ten, sa̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠ na̠ A̠meri onweni ta̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Asalomi, igho ma̠ i̠gho̠gho̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ eduduom ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 2 Obom ogbo asi̠ro̠ i̠b̠ala A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠, sa̠ awa iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogogo bho̠ a̠pu na̠ a̠mite bho̠.  
\v 3 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠pura̠n odi ma̠a̠, “A̠nyen ta̠ a̠kikiligi ma̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠ asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ od̠i bho̠?”  
\v 4 Sa̠ awa ikpon d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ bha̠ na̠ okikiligi ma̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠ o̠si̠ghe̠. Ezin bho̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠ abu̠gh ibom.  
\v 5 Sa̠ awa id̠igh d̠a̠ ologi od̠i bho̠ i̠bi̠gh o̠nyi̠ oyel ola̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agba bho̠, ibura̠ bho̠ na̠ esosorogia̠n, sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa.  
\v 6 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko o̠ku̠nu̠! Inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anazare̠t bho̠, wa̠ u̠du̠ ugigh d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠. I̠na na̠ b̠etina̠. I̠na bo̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n! I̠bi̠ghe̠ ma̠ esi bho̠ u̠mu̠ni̠e̠ni̠ i̠na bho̠.  
\v 7 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠gi̠e̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ i̠na A̠puta̠ ma̠a̠, ‘I̠na na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh, na̠ a̠ten na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili ka̠ ob̠a̠ra̠ inyin. Obha̠ esi inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠na, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ inyin bho̠.’ ” 
\p  
\v 8 Sa̠ awa ighil i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠ d̠a̠ ekpoyogha̠n ologi na̠ a̠rugugu. Ya̠a̠, awa i̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ abar enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, ma̠ ebula̠ a̠rugugu.\f + \fr 16:8 \ft Idi robhurugho bho̠ i̠lo̠gh ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ro̠go̠go̠ 9-20. Ikunugiom d̠a̠ wa̠leghemeni o̠bhabhanya (8) o̠go̠go̠ bho̠. \f* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 28:9,10; Azo̠n 20:11-18) 
\p [ 
\v 9 Obhel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠, ma̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠ d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r a̠d̠a̠ma̠ d̠a̠ esi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, bha̠ i̠na a̠d̠ia̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠, ani̠ wa̠ i̠na a̠ze ma̠ od̠ua̠l i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠.  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ten agi̠ ka̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ na̠ ed̠i bho̠.  
\v 11 Sa̠ obhel bho̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠, ya̠ ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ abi̠gh bho̠, ku̠ku̠m eka̠ awa id̠umom d̠o̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ i̠wal ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (A̠luk 24:13-35) 
\p  
\v 12 Onon a̠ten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ i̠wal ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ opa̠n a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ awa na̠ erile na̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ odi o̠gbara e̠ma.  
\v 13 Sa̠ awa imula̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠gba inigha̠ ma̠ iyed̠i, ku̠ku̠m eka̠, id̠umom d̠o̠ awa. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom Ogbo Ogir bho̠  //  ma̠ o̠gba Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 28:16-20; A̠luk 24:36-49; Azo̠n 20:19-23; Rogir 1:6-8) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ onin bho̠ ma̠ obhel ola̠ awa na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, sa̠ ali̠o̠m awa ma̠ ebula̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa od̠umom d̠o̠ bho̠. Ezin bho̠ awa ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo iya̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠na d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠.  
\v 15 Sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠a̠: \wj “I̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ ma̠ enigha̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ sa̠ uwur amu̠m bha̠ oten, ya̠a̠ ola̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ bha̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ebhum ase̠.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Sa̠ relegh i̠nye̠n ta̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m ogbo ya̠ id̠umom bho̠; d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠, awa ta̠ eze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh, sa̠ ta̠ efugh irorua̠ aru̠nu̠ e̠ma,\wj* 
\v 18 \wj sa̠ awa ta̠ ebhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa esibhi ma̠ i̠karabh i̠di̠ar, ya̠a̠ abar ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ awa, sa̠ ka̠ awa i̠d̠a ma̠ abar ola̠ na̠ a̠gigh o̠ni̠ eka̠, abar ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ awa, ta̠ e̠gbam aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r, sa̠ awa ta̠ ed̠um.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhun d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny 
\r (A̠luk 24:50-53; Rogir 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 19 Igiel bho̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠nigha̠ awa awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ ubhin i̠na ubhuneni d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, sa̠ i̠na ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 20 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iten imite ka̠ i̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ kesi kesi, sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ awa a̠gir, sa̠ a̠muzoghod̠iom o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠ na̠ ogir ilologia̠n.]